ries-educational-organization%2F32551047.html%230_8_10089_8766_2710_249306403%5C%22%3Emultiple%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Feurope%2Flive-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-news-08-16-23%3Futm_source%3Dtrendbar%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entity%20appears%20to%20be%20registered%20in%20the%20country's%20central%20Asipovichy%20district%2C%20which%20is%20the%20location%20of%20a%20military%20base%20where%20the%20mercenaries%20have%20been%20staying%20for%20several%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20inciting%20a%20deadly%20and%20short-lived%20armed%20rebellion%20against%20Russia's%20military%20leadership%20in%20late%20June%2C%20Wagner%20Group%20leader%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin%20was%20seemingly%20cast%20into%20exile%20in%20Belarus.%20Facing%20an%20uncertain%20future%2C%20Prigozhin's%20mercenaries%20were%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20join%20him%20in%20neighboring%20Belarus%2C%20which%20offered%20to%20host%20the%20fighters%20at%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-image-prigozhin-wagner-group-boss-maybe-at-belarus-camp-2023-7%5C%22%3Eabandoned%20military%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20Asipovichy%20region%20so%20they%20could%20train%20the%20country's%20armed%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelarus%20announced%20in%20mid-July%20that%20Wagner%20had%20started%20training%20territorial%20defense%20units%2C%20and%20that%20partnership%20has%20since%20expanded.%20The%20mercenaries%20eventually%20began%20to%20carry%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwagner-mercenaries-train-belarus-troops-russia-putin-grip-power-slipping-2023-8%5C%22%3Emore%20advanced%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20covering%20combined%20arms%20assault%20with%20tanks%20and%20artillery%20support%2C%20drone%20evasion%2C%20dismounted%20infantry%20maneuvering%2C%20and%20more.%20Experts%20have%20noted%20that%20some%20of%20these%20exercises%20typically%20take%20place%20in%20partnership%20with%20Ru