problems%20across%20both%20classes%20with%20the%20propulsion%20system%2C%20and%20the%20ships%20are%20almost%20as%20expensive%20to%20operate%20as%20a%20destroyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacing%20these%20problems%2C%20the%20Navy%20has%20pushed%20to%20divest%20of%20these%20platforms%20to%20save%20money%20on%20repairs%20and%20upgrades%20and%20is%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-started-building-its-new-constellation-class-frigates-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20platforms%20like%20its%20upcoming%20frigate%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20execute%20key%20missions%20the%20LCS%20was%20unable%20to%20handle%2C%20such%20as%20anti-submarine%20warfare.%20The%20Sioux%20City%20is%20just%20one%20of%20a%20number%20of%20Littoral%20Combat%20Ships%20the%20Navy%20seeks%20to%20decommission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224776%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Littoral%20combat%20ship%20USS%20Sioux%20City%20(LCS%2011)%20conducts%20a%20passing%20exercise%20with%20Egyptian%20Navy%20frigate%20ENS%20Alexandria%20(F%20911)%20while%20transiting%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20July%2030%2C%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dd17f2bd8c0900184e655f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223184%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUSS%20Sioux%20City%20conducts%20a%20passing%20exercise%20with%20an%20Egyptian%20Navy%20frigate%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%20July%202022.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%203rd%20Class%20Nicholas%20A.%20Russell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESioux%20City%20Mayor%20Bob%20Scott%20expressed%20frustration%20with%20the%20decision%20to%20decommission%20the%20ship%20named%20after%20his%20city%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iowapublicradio.org%2Fipr-news%2F2023-08-14%2Fsioux-city-mayor-condemns-the-navy-after-it-decommissions-the-uss-sioux-city%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%3C%2Fa%3E%20Iowa%20Public%20Radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20called%20the%20ship's%20commissioning%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20proudest%20days%20of%20Sioux%20City%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20all%20kinds%20of%20Sioux%20City%20citizens%20there%20because%20the%20community%20got%20behind%20that%20did%20a%20great%20job%20of%20showing%20the%20Navy%20how%20proud%20we%20were%20to%20have%20a%20ship%20named%20after%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Navy%20does%20to%20us%20in%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20calling%20the%20move%20a%20%26quot%3Bjoke.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B%20to%20spend%20%24350%20million%20on%20the%20ship%20knowing%20that%20the%20Littoral%20Combat%20Ships%20were%20%26quot%3Bsupposedly%20a%20problem%20and%20wasting%20taxpayers'%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sailor%20manning%20the%20lines%20as%20the%20Freedom-variant%20littoral%20combat%20ship%20USS%20Sioux%20City%20(LCS%2011)%20got%20underway%20for%20its%20first%20deployment%20in%20August%202020.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dd1da2bd8c0900184e72c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sailor%20aboard%20USS%20Sioux%20City%20as%20it%20gets%20underway%20for%20its%20first%20deployment%20in%20August%202020.%3Cp%3EUSS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%20Seaman%20Juel%20Foster%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20observers%20suggested%20throwing%20away%20ships%20doesn't%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20sense%20when%20the%20US%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-has-advantage-over-the-us-in-shipbuilding-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efalling%20behind%20its%20primary%20rival%2C%20China%2C%20in%20numbers%20of%20warships%20being%20built%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHard%20to%20figure%20this%20one%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20retired%20Navy%20Adm.%20James%20Stavridis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstavridisj%2Fstatus%2F1691834198007357693%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BHate%20to%20see%20anything%20decommissioned%20when%20we%20are%20so%20far%20behind%20China%20in%20overall%20ship%20count.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECounterarguments%20have%20been%20that%20the%20US%20needs%20to%20focus%20its%20attention%20on%20fielding%20systems%20that%20are%20survivable%20in%20a%2021st-century%20fight%20against%20a%20capable%20adversary%2C%20even%20if%20that%20requires%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.usni.org%2F2023%2F06%2F12%2Fhasc-agrees-to-navys-plans-to-shed-littoral-combat-ships-moves-to-abolish-cape%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etough%20calls%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStavridis%20said%20that%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20the%20US%20should%20transfer%20the%20ship%20to%20a%20partner%20navy%2C%20which%20is%20something%20the%20Navy%20has%20looked%20at%20doing%20with%20unwanted%20Littoral%20Combat%20Ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20decommissioning%20of%20the%20roughly%204%2C000-ton%20Sioux%20City%20that%20the%20vessel%20will%20be%20put%20in%20a%20%26quot%3BForeign%20Military%20Sale%20disposition%20status%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20its%20crew%20will%20receive%20new%20naval%20assignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-lcs-warship-just-decommissioned-after-short-service-life-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692217956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dcf9fdbd8c0900184e2d0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-lcs-warship-just-