r%20them%2C%20they%20didn't%20get%20an%20apology%20and%20had%20to%20foot%20the%20high%20medical%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%40airvistara%20%C2%A0air%20hostess%20causes%202nd%20degree%20burn%20to%2010%20year%20old%20on%20flight%20to%20Frankfurt.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20unfortunate%20accident%20poorly%20handled.%20Vistara%20hostess%20didn't%20apologize%2C%20captain%20or%20crew%20members%20didn't%20apologize%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gupta%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20basic%20first%20aid%20on%20flight%20my%20daughter%20and%20I%20were%20left%20in%20an%20ambulance%20to%20fend%20for%20ourselves%20(pay%20for%20ambulance%20%2F%20navigate%20the%20German%20medical%20emergency%20services)%20in%20an%20unfamiliar%20environment.%20Our%20luggage%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20out%20by%20friend%20of%20a%20friend%20who%20made%203%20trips%20to%20the%20airport%20and%20spent%204-5%20hours%20pillar%20to%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gupta%20said%20she%20had%20to%20pay%20the%20ambulance%20bill%20of%20503%20Euros%20as%20well%20as%20the%20hospital%20bill.%20She%20said%20they%20missed%20their%20connecting%20flight%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20airline%20did%20not%20make%20efforts%20to%20arrange%20an%20alternate%20flight%20for%20them.%20She%20claimed%20that%20the%20airline%20did%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20her%2C%20but%20only%20after%20her%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20statement%2C%20Air%20Vistara%20clarified%20that%20they%20have%20already%20facilitated%20the%20mother%20and%20daughter's%20return%20to%20India%20and%20are%20reviewing%20their%20processes%20to%20ensure%20such%20situations%20are%20avoided%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20confirm%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%20occured%20onboard%20UK25%20flying%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Frankfurt%20on%2011%20August%2C%202023%2C%20where%20a%20child%20sustained%20injuries%20due%20to%20spillage%20of%20hot%20beverage%20on%20the%20body.%20Our%20cabin%20crew%20had%20served%20hot%20chocolate%20to%20the%20child%20on%20the%20request%20of%20her%20parents%2C%20however%2C%20the%20hot%20water%20spilled%20on%20her%20since%20the%20child%20was%20playful%20during%20the%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline's%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20said%20that%20the%20girl%20was%20given%20first-aid%20and%20support%20was%20sought%20from%20a%20paramedic%20onboard%2C%20who%20volunteered%20to%20assist%20until%20the%20flight%20landed%20in%20Frankfurt.%20Medical%20care%20was%20also%20ensured%20upon%20landing%20by%20arranging%20an%20ambulance%20for%20the%20child%20and%20sending%20her%20and%20her%20mother%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20teams%20have%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20customer%20ever%20since.%20We%20have%20already%20facilitated%20their%20early%20return%20to%20India%2C%20arranged%20for%20ground%20transportation%20in%20Frankfurt%2C%20met%20them%20at%20the%20airport%20and%20extended%20extensive%20on-ground%20support.%20We%20have%20conveyed%20to%20the%20customer%20that%20all%20medical%20expenses%20arising%20from%20this%20incident%20will%20be%20reimbursed%20by%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20Vistara%20reiterated%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20in%20touch%20with%20family%20to%20provide%20any%20assistance%20that%20is%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20reviewing%20and%20refining%20our%20processes%2C%20wherever%20required%2C%20to%20ensure%20such%20situations%20are%20avoided%20in%20the%20future.%20As%20always%2C%20safety%20and%20comfort%20of%20our%20customers%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692212220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fqm26llk_plane-generic-_625x300_26_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n