to%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20She%20had%20gone%20missing%2C%20after%20which%20her%20parents%20filed%20a%20police%20case%20of%20kidnapping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20saw%20her%20with%20the%20teen%20at%20Bandra%20terminus%2C%20and%20they%20caught%20hold%20of%20him.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20shows%20the%20teen%20being%20kicked%2C%20punched%20and%20dragged%20by%20the%20group%20of%20men.%20They%20took%20him%20outside%20the%20railway%20station%20and%20thrashed%20him%20there%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20then%20handed%20over%20the%20girl%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20police%20haven't%20given%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20incident%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bandra%20Railway%20Police%2C%20however%2C%20said%20they%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20unknown%20people%20for%20assaulting%20the%20teen%20and%20raising%20objectionable%20slogans%20under%20the%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bandra%20railway%20police%20(GRP)%20officer%20said%20that%20after%20receiving%20a%20letter%20from%20Nirmal%20Nagar%20police%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20for%20rioting%20and%20assault%20was%20filed%20against%20unknown%20people%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20GRP%20is%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%20as%20it%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20the%20incident...%20We%20have%20identified%20the%20assaulted%20boy%20and%20contacted%20his%20family%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20who%20assaulted%20the%20boy%20can%20be%20clearly%20seen%20in%20the%20viral%20video%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20no%20arrest%20has%20been%20made%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692208620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F8bfst5d8_man-thrashed-mumbai_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%