cks%2Fcommercial-real-estate-crash-bank-lending-credit-crunch-prices-rates-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHigh%20interest%20rates%2C%20uncertainty%20about%20property%20values%2C%20and%20questions%20about%20some%20property%20fundamentals%20are%20all%20contributing%20to%20the%20slowdown.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcommercial-real-estate-crash-bank-lending-credit-crunch-prices-rates-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chest%20Measurement%20Criterion%20For%20Women%20For%20Any%20Post%20%5C%22Outrageous%5C%22%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court%20has%20denounced%20the%20criterion%20of%20chest%20measurement%20to%20gauge%20the%20lung%20capacity%20of%20female%20candidates%20during%20physical%20examination%20in%20recruitment%20process%20for%20foresters%20%26quot%3Bor%20any%20other%20post%26quot%3B%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20absolutely%20arbitrary%20and%20outrageous%20and%20dents%20a%20woman's%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20directed%20the%20state%20authorities%20to%20seek%20opinions%20of%20experts%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20any%20alternative%20means%20to%20determine%20the%20desired%20level%20of%20lung%20capacity%20%26quot%3Bto%20avoid%20this%20unwarranted%20humiliation%20of%20women%20candidates%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Dinesh%20Mehta%20made%20the%20observation%20while%20deciding%20a%20petition%20by%20three%20female%20candidates%20challenging%20their%20disqualification%20on%20the%20parameter%20of%20chest%20measurement%20despite%20clearing%20the%20Physical%20Efficiency%20Test%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Forest%20Guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20preferred%20not%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process%2C%20which%20had%20already%20taken%20place%2C%20but%20stated%20%E2%80%9Csome%20deliberation%20is%20necessary%20about%20the%20very%20requirement%20of%20chest%20measurement%20for%20the%20female%20candidates%2C%20may%20it%20be%20for%20the%20recruitment%20of%20Forest%20Guard%20or%20Forester%20or%20any%20other%20post%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20size%20of%20the%20chest%20and%20its%20expansion%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20female%20candidate%20may%20not%20necessarily%20be%20a%20pointer%20of%20physical%20fitness%20and%20a%20litmus%20test%20of%20the%20lungs'%20capacity%2C%20the%20judge%20observed%20in%20the%20August%2010%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20it%20be%20so%2C%20such%20measurement%20impinges%20upon%20or%20intrudes%20on%20the%20privacy%20of%20a%20female.%20Apart%20from%20being%20irrational%2C%20prescribing%20such%20criterion%20disrupts%20the%20dignity%2C%20bodily%20autonomy%20and%20mental%20integrity%20of%20a%20woman%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20court%20stated%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20criterion%20is%20absolutely%20arbitrary%20and%20outrageous%20and%20a%20clear%20dent%20on%20a%20woman's%20dignity%20and%20right%20to%20privacy%20guaranteed%20under%20Articles%2014%20and%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20told%20the%20court%20that%20their%20measurement%20was%20more%20than%20required%20after%20which%20the%20high%20court%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20the%20medical%20board%20of%20AIIMS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20however%2C%20stated%20that%20two%20candidates'%20chest%20measurements%20were%20less%20than%20required%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bnormal%20condition%26quot%3B%20while%20one%20of%20them%20had%20chest%20measurement%20less%20than%20required%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bexpanded%20condition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20this%20report%2C%20the%20court%20rejected%20their%20petitions%20and%20upheld%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20recruiting%20agency%20to%20disqualify%20them%2C%20but%20objected%20to%20the%20use%20of%20chest%20measurement%20among%20female%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20order%20was%20marked%20to%20the%20state%20chief%20secretary%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20and%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20department%20of%20personnel%20to%20have%20a%20relook%20into%20this%20criterion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20them%20to%20solicit%20the%20opinion%20of%20experts%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20alternative%20means%20to%20determine%20the%20desired%20level%20of%20lung%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692208260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchest-measurement-criterion-for-women-for-any-post-outrageous-rajasthan-high-court-4303621%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court%20has%20denounced%20the%20criterion%20of%20chest%20measurement%20to%20gauge%20the%20lung%20capacity%20of%20female%20candidates%20during%20physical%20examination%20in%20recruitment%20process%20for%20%26quot%3Bany%20other%20post%26quot%3B%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20absolutely%20arbitrary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchest-measurement-criterion-for-women-for-any-post-outrageous-rajasthan-high-court-4303621%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchest-measurement-criterion-for-women-for-any-post-outrageous-rajasthan-high-court-4303621%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchest-measurement-criterion-for-women-for-any-post-outrageous-rajasthan-high-court-4303621%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Brooklyn%20land