0one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20tourist%20sites%20across%20Indian.%20People%20love%20to%20keep%20click%20a%20photo%20with%20the%20structure.%20However%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20in%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20complex%20people%20were%20more%20intrigued%20to%20click%20photos%20with%20a%20different%20object%20-%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20only%2050%20days%20remaining%20to%20go%20for%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20eagerly%20anticipated%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20prestigious%20trophy%20was%20proudly%20displayed%20at%20the%20enchanting%C2%A0Taj%C2%A0Mahal%C2%A0in%20Agra%2C%20India.%20The%20gleaming%20silverware%2C%20set%20to%20be%20the%20ultimate%20prize%20when%20the%20tournament%20gets%20underway%20from%205%20October%20to%2019%20November%2C%20radiated%20under%20the%20sun%20against%20the%20magnificent%20backdrop%20of%20the%C2%A0Taj%C2%A0Mahal%E2%80%94a%20true%20Wonder%20of%20the%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUP%20%7C%20ICC%20Men's%20World%20Cup%20trophy%20displayed%20at%20Taj%20Mahal%20in%20Agra%20today%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqRCuMKAznF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqRCuMKAznF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20UP%2FUttarakhand%20(%40ANINewsUP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANINewsUP%2Fstatus%2F1691819868969197749%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%C2%A0Taj%C2%A0Mahal%C2%A0symbolized%20a%20harmonious%20blend%20of%20India's%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20cricket%2C%20offering%20an%20exquisite%20spectacle%20for%20fans%20as%20the%20tournament's%20excitement%20continues%20to%20build.%20The%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20Trophy%20Tour%20aims%20to%20capture%20the%20festive%20and%20celebratory%20spirit%20associated%20with%20Cricket%20World%20Cups%2C%20presenting%20a%20series%20of%20grand%20events%20at%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20iconic%20destinations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%209%2C%20ICC%20released%20a%20statement%20to%20announce%20the%20revised%20schedule%20for%20the%20upcoming%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20much-awaited%20encounter%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20has%20been%20rescheduled%20to%20a%20different%20day%2C%20along%20with%20this%20eight%20other%20matches%20of%20the%20tournament%20have%20also%20been%20changed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clash%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20was%20originally%20slated%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Sunday%2C%20October%2015%2C%20but%20this%20clash%20has%20been%20moved%20a%20day%20earlier%20and%20will%20now%20be%20held%20at%20the%20same%20venue%20on%20Saturday%2C%20October%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20England's%20fixture%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%20Delhi%20will%20be%20moved%20from%20Saturday%2C%20October%2014%20and%20will%20now%20be%20played%2024%20hours%20later%20on%20Sunday%2C%20October%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20contest%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Hyderabad%20has%20moved%20from%20Thursday%2C%2012%20October%20to%20now%20being%20played%20on%20Tuesday%2C%2010%20October%20and%20Australia's%20big%20match%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20Lucknow%20moved%20back%2024%20hours%20and%20will%20now%20be%20played%20on%20Thursday%2C%20October%2012%20instead%20of%20Friday%2C%20October%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692201000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fa9gg0r2o_world-cup-taj-mahal-_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc