%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692200499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F20%2Ffull%2F1689869491-9008.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcabinet-approves-rs-14-903-cr-for-ai-cybersecurity-digital-skilling-123081600710_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20previously%20revealed%20plans%20to%20construct%20three%20Centres%20of%20Excellence%20(CoE)%20for%20the%20advancement%20of%20AI%20research%20and%20innovation%20in%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcabinet-approves-rs-14-903-cr-for-ai-cybersecurity-digital-skilling-123081600710_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcabinet-approves-rs-14-903-cr-for-ai-cybersecurity-digital-skilling-123081600710_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcabinet-approves-rs-14-903-cr-for-ai-cybersecurity-digital-skilling-123081600710_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nuh%20Violence%20Accused%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%2C%20Aides%20Waved%20Swords%2C%20Tridents%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20strict%20order%20against%20carrying%20weapons%2C%20Haryana%20violence%20accused%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20and%20nearly%2020%20other%20people%20not%20only%20waved%20swords%20and%20tridents%2C%20but%20also%20snatched%20them%20away%20from%20the%20police%20after%20they%20were%20confiscated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20startling%20fact%2C%20and%20several%20others%20like%20it%2C%20have%20emerged%20from%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20filed%20against%20the%20cow%20vigilante%20and%20his%20associates%20by%20the%20Nuh%20assistant%20superintendent%20of%20police.%20Bajrangi%20was%20arrested%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20complaint%20yesterday%20and%20has%20been%20remanded%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20states%20that%20on%20July%2031%2C%20the%20day%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Nuh%20during%20the%20Jal%20Abhishek%20Yatra%20organised%20by%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Usha%20Kundu%20was%20checking%20cars%20as%20part%20of%20the%20police's%20security%20measures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kundu%20says%20in%20the%20FIR%20that%2C%20around%2012.30%20pm%2C%20she%20was%20about%20300%20metres%20from%20the%20Nalhar%20Shiv%20Temple%20in%20Nuh%20when%20she%20saw%20Bajrangi%20and%2015-20%20other%20people%20heading%20towards%20the%20temple%20with%20tridents%20and%20swords.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kundu%20said%20that%20when%20she%20and%20her%20colleagues%20tried%20to%20take%20the%20weapons%20away%20from%20the%20men%2C%20they%20began%20raising%20slogans%20against%20the%20police%20and%20even%20manhandled%20some%20of%20the%20personnel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20the%20weapons%20from%20them%20and%20kept%20them%20in%20the%20police%20van.%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20and%20his%20companions%20sat%20in%20front%20of%20my%20official%20vehicle%20and%20started%20raising%20slogans%20against%20the%20police.%20Some%20time%20later%2C%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20and%20his%20aides%20snatched%20away%20the%20swords%20and%20trident-like%20weapons%20by%20opening%20the%20rear%20window%20of%20the%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20FIR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kundu%20said%20Bajrangi%20and%20his%20associates%20acted%20illegally%20by%20possessing%20illegal%20weapons%2C%20obstructing%20the%20police%20in%20their%20duty%2C%20threatening%20the%20police%20and%20snatching%20away%20the%20weapons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20registered%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20pertaining%20to%20rioting%20armed%20with%20deadly%20weapons%2C%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20voluntarily%20causing%20hurt%20to%20deter%20public%20servants%20from%20their%20duty%2C%20assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20public%20servants%2C%20obstructing%20a%20public%20servant%20from%20discharging%20duty%2C%20and%20criminal%20intimidation.%20Provisions%20of%20the%20Arms%20Act%20were%20also%20invoked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrangi%20is%20known%20to%20be%20an%20aide%20of%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leader%20Monu%20Manesar%2C%20who%20is%20wanted%20for%20two%20murders%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20is%20also%20under%20the%20scanner%20in%20the%20Nuh%20violence%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrangi%2C%20who%20heads%20a%20cow%20vigilante%20group%20in%20Faridabad%2C%20is%20also%20accused%20of%20stoking%20communal%20tension%20ahead%20of%20the%20July%2031%20march%20and%20had%20been%20arrested%20on%20August%204.%20He%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20yesterday.%20Hearing%20the%20case%20today%2C%20a%20court%20in%20Nuh%20remanded%20him%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%20which%20broke%20out%20in%20Nuh%20and%20spread%20to%20adjoining%20areas%2C%20including%20Gurugram.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692200220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frl8uq6s8_bittu-bajrangi_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbittu-bajrangi-aides-were-headed-to-temple-with-swords-tridents-complaint-4303523%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20a%20strict%20order%20against%20carrying%20weapons%2C%20Haryana%20violence%20accused%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20and%20nearly%2020%20other%20people%20not%20only%20waved%20swords%20and%20tridents%2C%20but%20also%20snatched%20them%20away%20from%20the%20police%20after%20they%20were%20confiscated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbittu-bajrangi-aides-were-headed-to-temple-with-swords-tridents-complaint-