n-spain%2Farticleshow%2F102778277.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fsix-arrested-over-sex-assault-of-british-woman-in-spain%2Famp_articleshow%2F102778277.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fsix-arrested-over-sex-assault-of-british-woman-in-spain%2Famp_articleshow%2F102778277.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20Faculty%20Member%20Volunteered'%20for%20Academic%20Freedom%20Body%2C%20Ashoka%20University%20VC%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16201010%2FAshoka.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Responding%20to%20a%20letter%20by%20Ashoka%20University%20faculty%20urging%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Committee%20for%20Academic%20Freedom%E2%80%99%20(CAF)%2C%20vice%20chancellor%20Somak%20Raychaudhury%20has%20said%20that%20previous%20attempts%20to%20form%20such%20a%20committee%20had%20failed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cno%20faculty%20member%20volunteered%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDated%20Sunday%20(August%2013)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fecon-dept-says-ashoka-governing-body-interference-forcing-scholars-to-operate-in-environment-of-fear%5C%22%3Ethe%20letter%20has%2082%20signatories%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20is%20addressed%20to%20the%20vice%20chancellor%20as%20well%20as%20to%20Amita%20Baviskar%2C%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20dean%20of%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20that%20having%20a%20CAF%20would%20prevent%20the%20university%20from%20making%20public%20pronouncements%20on%20academic%20freedom%20whose%20origins%20other%20university%20stakeholders%20may%20not%20have%20had%20a%20say%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%E2%80%99s%20authors%20also%20note%20that%20a%202021%20university%20document%20on%20academic%20freedom%20had%20proposed%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20CAF%2C%20and%20that%20this%20document%20had%20been%20adopted%20into%20a%20handbook%20on%20faculty%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20ask%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20the%20Committee%20for%20Academic%20Freedom%2C%20which%20the%20document%20had%20proposed%20be%20set%20up%20soon%2C%20be%20created%20immediately.%20It%20will%20bring%20much-needed%20transparency%20and%20procedural%20fairness%20whenever%20such%20issues%20arise%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20also%20prevent%2C%20on%20such%20occasions%2C%20public%20pronouncements%20that%20claim%20to%20speak%20on%20behalf%20of%20Ashoka%20University%20of%20whose%20provenance%20almost%20no%20one%20at%20the%20university%20is%20aware.%20All%20such%20pronouncements%20and%20decisions%20about%20actions%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20such%20circumstances%20should%20emanate%2C%20after%20deliberation%2C%20from%20the%20Committee%20for%20Academic%20Freedom%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continues%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELetter%20on%20Academic%20Freedom%20by%20Members%20of%20the%20Faculty%2C%20Ashoka%20University.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4rIROaMPhh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4rIROaMPhh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Saikat%20Majumdar%20(%40_saikatmajumdar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_saikatmajumdar%2Fstatus%2F1691472817756254209%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Raychaudhury%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20faculty%20and%20students%20that%20attempts%20to%20form%20a%20CAF%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20had%20been%20unsuccessful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20stated%20in%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20Academic%20Council%20yesterday%20%5BAugust%2014%5D%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20appeal%20to%20us%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Committee%20for%20Academic%20Freedom%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20in%20his%20email%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20understand%2C%20even%20though%20it%20was%20proposed%20by%20the%20Dean%20of%20Faculty%20several%20times%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20Committee%20could%20not%20be%20formed%2C%20because%20no%20faculty%20member%20volunteered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20faculty%20member%20who%20sent%20the%20letter%20wrote%20that%20in%20the%20aforementioned%20academic%20council%20meeting%2C%20Raychaudhury%20and%20Baviskar%20agreed%20on%20the%20necessity%20for%20a%20CAF%20and%20asked%20that%20it%20be%20set%20up%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20delay%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20professor%20also%20said%20that%20a%20process%20for%20putting%20a%20CAF%20in%20place%20had%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Raychaudhury%20said%20in%20his%20email%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20that%20measures%20are%20now%20being%20taken%20to%20form%20this%20committee%2C%20and%20you%20have%20my%20full%20support%20to%20create%20it%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20following%20the%20guidelines%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20Faculty%20handbook.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20243px)%2085vw%2C%20243px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16193450%2FSabyasachi-Das-150x150.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22243%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16193450%2FSabyasachi-Das-292x300.png%20292w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16193450%2FSabyasachi-Das.png%20400w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr%20Sabyasachi%20Das.%20Photo%3A%20ashoka.edu.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshoka%20University%20has%20become%20embroiled%20in%20a