%2C%20Properties%20In%20India%3A%20High-Profile%20Thief%20Caught%20In%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20high-profile%20thief%20who%20owns%20a%20hotel%20in%20Nepal%20and%20has%20several%20properties%20in%20his%20name%20in%20India%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20Manoj%20Chaubey%2C%20who%20has%20confessed%20to%20more%20than%20200%20thefts%2C%20reminds%20of%20another%20notorious%20thief%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20around%20500%20cases%20of%20theft%20across%20the%20country%20and%20even%20inspired%20a%20hit%20Bollywood%20film%20-%20'Oye%20Lucky!%20Lucky%20Oye!'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2048-year-old%20has%20two%20wives%20-%20one%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20the%20other%20in%20Delhi%20-%20but%20neither%20of%20them%20knew%20he%20was%20a%20thief%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChaubey%20is%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Siddharth%20Nagar%20who%20would%20come%20to%20Delhi%20to%20commit%20theft.%20He%20was%20arrested%20from%20Karawal%20Nagar%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jitendra%20Kumar%20Meena%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20of%20northwest%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20to%20Delhi%20in%201997%20and%20was%20first%20caught%20for%20theft%20in%20a%20canteen%2C%20police%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20houses%20in%20posh%20areas%20were%20his%20main%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoubey%20built%20a%20hotel%20in%20Nepal%20with%20the%20stolen%20money%20and%20bought%20a%20guest%20house%20for%20one%20of%20his%20wives%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20police%20said.%20He%20even%20bought%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20the%20same%20area%20and%20leased%20it%20to%20a%20hospital%20at%20a%20monthly%20rent%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%2C%20police%20said.%20He%20has%20a%20house%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20his%20children%20study%20in%20a%20reputed%20school%20in%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20caught%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20at%20least%20nine%20times%20but%20escaped%20every%20time.%20This%20time%20ar