ul%20Dravid%20admitted%20that%20there's%20a%20shortfall%20of%20all-rounders%20in%20the%20team.%20The%205th%20T20I%20between%20India%20and%20West%20Indies%20even%20saw%20Tilak%20Varma%20bowl%2C%20taking%20the%20prized%20wicket%20of%20Nicholas%20Pooran.%20While%20Varma%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20have%20been%20backed%20to%20bowl%20more%20often%20by%20the%20Indian%20team%20management%2C%20even%20former%20cricketers%20are%20lining%20up%2C%20backing%20this%20approach%20by%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricketer%20Aakash%20Chopra%20called%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%20to%20push%20for%20batters%20who%20can%20bowl%20and%20give%20youngsters%20like%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Tilak%20Varma%20a%20long%20rope%20and%20encouragement%20to%20bowl%20as%20often%20as%20possible.%C2%A0He%20also%20called%20for%20spin-bowling%20all-rounder%20Washington%20Sundar%20to%20become%20a%20part%20of%20India's%20scheme%20of%20things%20in%20T20I%20format.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20that%20most%20of%20the%20current%20Indian%20batters%20don't%20bowl%20even%20a%20couple%20of%20overs%2C%20Indian%20team%20must%20start%20pushing%20for%20batters%20who%20do.%20Yashasvi-Tilak%20should%20be%20given%20a%20longer%20rope%E2%80%A6and%20encouraged%20to%20bowl%20as%20often%20as%20possible.%20Washington%20has%20to%20be%20in%20India's%20T20%20scheme%20of%20things%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chopra%20in%20a%20tweet%20on%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EConsidering%20that%20most%20of%20the%20current%20Indian%20batters%20don't%20bowl%20even%20a%20couple%20of%20overs%2C%20Indian%20team%20must%20start%20pushing%20for%20batters%20who%20do.%20Yashasvi-Tilak%20should%20be%20given%20a%20longer%20rope%E2%80%A6and%20encouraged%20to%20bowl%20as%20often%20as%20possible.%20Washington%20has%20to%20be%20in%20India's%20T20%20scheme%20of%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Aakash%20Chopra%20(%40cricketaakash)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcricketaakash%2Fstatus%2F1691645359137984715%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20stars%20like%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(11%20international%20wickets)%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20(eight%20international%20wickets)%20have%20not%20bowled%20since%20years%20despite%20rolling%20their%20arms%20a%20bit%20in%20their%20initial%20years%2C%20causing%20the%20team%20to%20lose%20out%20on%20the%20variety%20and%20options%20that%20they%20could%20have%20offered%20with%20their%20part-time%20bowling.%20Also%2C%20newer%20stars%20like%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20have%20played%20as%20specialist%20batters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20was%20not%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20of%20the%20old%20days%2C%20with%20batting%20stars%20like%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20(201%20international%20wickets)%2C%20Virender%20Sehwag%20(136%20international%20wickets)%2C%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20(132%20international%20wickets)%2C%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20(148%20international%20wickets)%20and%20Suresh%20Raina%20(62%20international%20wickets)%20being%20extremely%20capable%20with%20the%20ball%20and%20had%20the%20ability%20to%20pick%20up%20crucial%20wickets%20just%20when%20their%20team%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20batters%20who%20can%20bowl%20has%20caused%20the%20team%20to%20be%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20their%20full-time%20bowlers%20like%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%2C%20Bhuvneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20Umran%20Malik%2C%20Umesh%20Yadav%20etc%20with%20all-rounders%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20bowling%20all-rounders%20Shardul%20Thakur%2C%20Axar%20Patel%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20being%20the%20only%20players%20providing%20the%20team%20with%20much-needed%20depth%20and%20options%20due%20to%20their%20capabilities%20and%20consistency%20with%20both%20bat%20and%20ball.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETilak%20(14%20wickets%20in%20first-class%2C%20List%20A%20and%20T20%20cricket)%20and%20Yashasvi%20(seven%20wickets%20across%20all%20formats%20at%20the%20domestic%20level)%20were%20given%20the%20ball%20during%20the%20final%20T20I%20against%20West%20Indies%2C%20which%20India%20lost.%20India%20lost%20the%20series%202-3.%20During%20the%20series%2C%20India's%20batting%20depth%20was%20a%20key%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20fourth%20T20I%20against%20the%20Windies%2C%20Indian%20bowling%20coach%20Paras%20Mhambrey%20had%20said%20that%20the%20team%20is%20working%20with%20Yashasvi%20and%20Tilak%20on%20their%20bowling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20someone%20who%20can%20chip%20in%2C%20it%20is%20nice.%20I%20have%20seen%20Tilak%20and%20Yashasvi%20bowl%20since%20U19%20days.%20They%20are%20capable%20of%20being%20good%20bowlers.%20They%20can%20work%20on%20it%20at%20this%20level.%20When%20you%20got%20options%20like%20these%2C%20it%20is%20nice%20to%20have%20them.%20We%20will%20see%20them%20bowl%20soon%20hopefully%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20it.%20It%20will%20take%20time.%20Soon%2C%20we%20will%20see%20them%20bowling%20an%20over%20at%20least%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paras%20in%20a%20pre-match%20press%20conference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20Sundar%2C%20he%20has%20played%20123%20T20s%20and%20scored%201%2C147%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2019.44%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20120%2C%20with%20three%20fifties%20in%2080%20innings.%20He%20also%20has%2093%20wickets%20in%20the%20format%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%203%2F10.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20he%20has%20played%2035%20T20Is%2C%20scoring%20107%20runs%20with%20a%20half-century%20and%20having%20taken%2029%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%