avatar-titanic-james-camerons-best-films%2Fphotostory%2F102775430.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102775430.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETerminator%2C%20Avatar%2C%20Titanic%3A%20James%20Cameron%E2%80%99s%20best%20films%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arjun%20Pereira%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fweb-stories%2Fterminator-avatar-titanic-james-camerons-best-films%2Fphotostory%2F102775430.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%20Nears%20Exciting%20Finish%2C%20Russia%20Joins%20Lunar%20Jugalbandi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20lunar%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20nearing%20its%20exciting%20climax.%20It%20is%20the%20closest%20to%20the%20moon%20before%20the%20tricky%20landing%20manoeuvre%20is%20attempted%20on%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20lunar%20probe%20Luna-25%2C%20too%2C%20is%20also%20closing%20in%20and%20will%20attempt%20a%20landing%20between%20August%2021%20and%2023.%20Both%20Russia%20and%20India%20are%20targeting%20to%20land%20nearer%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20an%20Indo-Russia%20race%20to%20the%20moon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20feels%20there%20is%20no%20such%20race.%20Both%20nations%20will%20have%20a%20new%20'meeting%20point'%20on%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20key%20details%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%20from%20Sriharikota%20using%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-3.%20It%20reached%20the%20moon's%20orbit%20on%20August%205%2C%20and%20has%20been%20orbiting%20it%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Chandryaan-3%20was%20put%20in%20an%20orbit%20of%20153%20km%20by%20163%20km%20and%20all%20lunar-bound%20manoeuvres%20were%20completed.%20On%20August%2017%2C%20the%20propulsion%20module%20and%20the%20lander%20Vikram%20will%20separate.%20The%20propulsion%20module%20will%20continue%20its%20journey%20in%20the%20same%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2023%2C%20after%20the%20preloaded%20commands%20are%20triggered%2C%20the%20lander%20Vikram%20will%20attempt%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface.%20ISRO%20has%20done%20many%20tests%20to%20ensure%20a%20failsafe%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20final%20backup%2C%20the%20lander%20Vikram%20has%20a%20'salvage%20mode'%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20lander%20touches%20down%20and%20the%20lunar%20dust%20settles%2C%20the%20Pragyaan%20rover%20will%20be%20rolled%20down.%20Lander%20Vikram%20will%20take%20images%20of%20the%20Pragyaan%20rover%20and%20the%20rover%20will%20take%20images%20of%20the%20lander%20-%20the%20first%20Indian%20selfies%20from%20the%20lunar%20surface%20will%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20then%2C%20the%2014%20Earth%20day%20planned%20scientific%20exploration%20of%20the%20moon%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20details%20of%20the%20Russian%20moon%20probe%20'Luna%2025'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20surprise%20move%2C%20Russia%20launched%20its%20lunar%20satellite%20named%20'Luna%2025'%20on%20August%2011%20-%2047%20years%20after%20the%20USSR%20last%20sent%20a%20lunar%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20used%20a%20heavy-lift%20rocket%20that%20sent%20the%20Luna%2025%20satellite%20directly%20on%20its%20journey%20to%20the%20moon%2C%20unlike%20India%20which%20used%20a%20circuitous%20slingshot%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Luna%2025%20probe%20is%20likely%20to%20enter%20the%20moon's%20orbit%20on%20August%2016.%20Russia%20seeks%20to%20attempt%20a%20soft%20landing%20between%20August%2021%20and%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Luna-25%20and%20Vikram%20are%20trying%20to%20land%20close%20to%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Luna%2025%20satellite%20weighed%201%2C750%20kg%20at%20lift-off%20and%20carries%2030%20kg%20of%20nine%20scientific%20experiments.%20It%20is%20only%20a%20robotic%20lander%20and%20has%20no%20rover%20in%20it.%20The%20expected%20mission%20life%20of%20Luna-25%20is%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuna%2025%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20radioactive%20generator%2C%20so%20it%20can%20last%20longer.%20Its%20journey%20from%20the%20Earth%20to%20the%20moon%20will%20last%2010%20days.%20The%20Russian%20spacecraft%20will%20conduct%20a%20study%20of%20the%20moon%20soil%20and%20look%20for%20water%20and%20ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComparison%3A%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20Luna%2025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20will%20take%2040%20days%20to%20reach%20the%20moon%20surface%2C%20while%20Luna%2025%20will%20take%20just%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20used%20a%20heavier%20rocket%2C%20so%20it%20could%20send%20its%20lunar%20satellite%20directly%20to%20the%20moon%3B%20India%20used%20a%20medium-lift%20rocket%20and%20took%20a%20circuitous%20route%3B%20Chandryaan-3%20weighs%203%2C921%20kg%20and%20Luna%2025%20weighs%201%2C750%20kg%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20carries%20both%20the%20lander%20Vikram%20the%20rover%20Pragyaan.%20Luna%2025%20is%20only%20a%20lander%20mission%2C%20without%20a%20rover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%20Vikram%20weighs%201%2C745%20kg%20and%20the%20Luna%2025%20lander%20weighs%20800%20kg.%20The%20expected%20mission%20life%20of%20Vikram%20lander%20is%2014%20Earth%20days%3B%20Luna%2025%20will%20last%20one%20year%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Russian%20and%20Indian%20lunar%20probes%20want%20to%20set%20the%20record%20of%20the%20first%20successful%20soft-landing%20near%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20purposefully%20crash-landed%20its%20moon%20impact%20probe%20as%20part%20of%20Chandryaan-1%20in%202