nt%20in%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time.%20I%20had%20short%20notes%20for%20every%20topic.%20Your%20content%20should%20be%20condensed.%20For%20example%2C%20convert%20a%2020%E2%80%9330%20page%20topic%20into%203%E2%80%934%20page%20short%20notes.%20Also%2C%20prepare%20yourself%20to%20appear%20to%20write%20general%20studies%20papers%201%2C%202%2C%203%2C%20and%204%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20four%20exams%20in%20two%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeep%20another%20career%20option%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20may%20meet%20many%20toppers%20and%20officers%20while%20preparing%2C%20but%20remember%20there%20are%20lakhs%20who%20were%20unable%20to%20clear%20the%20exam.%20Their%20stories%20never%20get%20published.%20Make%20sure%20to%20meet%20them%20and%20understand%20the%20challenges%20they%20faced.%20Then%20focus%20on%20the%20exam%20sincerely.%20There%20is%20no%20shame%20in%20having%20a%20second%20career%20option%3B%20IITians%20also%20keep%20NIT%20as%20an%20option!%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20make%20exam%20your%20life%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20a%20test%2C%20not%20your%20entire%20life.%20You%20might%20excel%20in%20your%20studies%20and%20preparation%2C%20but%20outcomes%20might%20not%20always%20go%20as%20planned.%20Many%20aspirants%20worry%20that%20failing%20this%20exam%20will%20ruin%20their%20lives.%20At%20times%2C%20this%20pressure%20leads%20us%20to%20answer%20questions%20incorrectly.%20Remember%20to%20stay%20calm%20during%20the%20exam.%20With%20patience%2C%20things%20will%20eventually%20work%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692194704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUPSC-2-1692192414.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Agra%E2%80%99s%20P