a%2Fstory%2Fus-delegation-india-visit-rahul-gandhi-meeting-indian-american-lawmakers-us-congressmen-2421317-2023-08-15%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20and%20the%20entire%20delegation%20are%20a%20guest%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%20It%20is%20for%20them%20to%20arrange%20that.%20I%20know%20that%20people%20have%20wanted%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20delegation%2C%20and%20I%20have%20conveyed%20those%20requests%20to%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20and%20would%20defer%20to%20their%20judgement.%20They%20have%20been%20incredibly%20gracious%20to%20us%20and%20have%20set%20up%20tremendous%20meetings.%20I%20want%20to%20respect%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20while%20speaking%20with%20the%20TV%20channel%2C%20senior%20Congress%20party%20official%20Praveen%20Chakravarty%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfew%20member%20of%20the%20US%20Congressmen%20delegation%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days%E2%80%9D%20to%20seek%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprivate%20meeting%E2%80%9D%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20had%20agreed%20to%20any%20such%20meeting%2C%20Chakravarty%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20asked%20them%20to%20make%20a%20formal%20and%20official%20request%20for%20the%20delegation%20to%20meet%20with%20Mr.%20Gandhi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20noted%20that%20the%20MEA%20should%20not%20have%20objected%20if%20a%20visiting%20delegation%20sought%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20principal%20leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20a%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20whether%20a%20green%20light%20%3Cspan%3Ewas%20given%20to%20a%20req%3C%2Fspan%3Euest%20for%20a%20meeting%20between%20the%20visiting%20congressional%20leaders%20and%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20MEA%20refused%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20his%20Twitter%20account%2C%20Khanna%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20San%20Francisco%2C%20shared%20the%20news%20report%20about%20the%20US%20delegation%20seeking%20a%20meeting%20with%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20batted%20criticism%20about%20meeting%20with%20a%20right-wing%20columnist%20Abhijit%20Iyer-Mitra%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20assailed%20his%20colleagues%20Ilhan%20Omar%20and%20Rashida%20Talib%20for%20boycotting%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20Washington.%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20see%20the%20totality%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20including%20meeting%20with%20activists%20and%20speaking%20out%20on%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRoKhanna%2Fstatus%2F1691654872733823341%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20replied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20another%20similar%20critical%20tweet%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRoKhanna%2Fstatus%2F1691708974322909353%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20wrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20wait%20until%20all%20the%20meetings%20we%20have%20had%20and%20conversations%20are%20public%20to%20make%20a%20final%20judgment.%20We%20have%20done%20a%20lot%20you%20will%20see%20to%20strengthen%20the%20relationship%20and%20advance%20democratic%20values%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRoKhanna%2Fstatus%2F1691524131714650112%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKhanna%20also%20wrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Mitra%20had%20%E2%80%9C%20sharply%20criticised%20my%20grandfather%20(see%20his%20past%20posts%20on%20me)%20and%20we%20met%20so%20I%20could%20stand%20up%20for%20my%20grandfather%20legacy%20as%20a%20freedom%20fighter.%20Gandhi%20had%20a%20philosophy%20of%20engaging%20with%20almost%20anyone%20%E2%80%93%20including%20British%20colonisers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20his%20arrival%20in%20India%2C%20Khanna%20had%20met%20with%20US-based%20civil%20rights%20groups%20and%20assured%20them%20that%20he%20would%20raise%20human%20rights%20concerns%20during%20his%20trip.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fro-khanna-india-independence-day%2F70528662007%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20speaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20August%209%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Khanna%20added%20that%20he%20respected%20his%20colleagues%20who%20boycotted%20the%20speech.%20During%20the%20India%20trip%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20convey%20the%20importances%20of%20pluralism%20and%20respecting%20minority%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20one%20can%20have%20two%20views%20that%20aren%E2%80%99t%20contradictory%20%E2%88%92%20that%20India%20is%20a%20very%20important%20partner%2C%20a%20very%20important%20democracy%20and%20yet%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperfect%20and%20that%20we%20have%20to%20be%20aspirational%20in%20making%20sure%20it%E2%80%99s%20pluralistic%20and%20respects%20minority%20rights%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20proved%20to%20its%20founding%20ideal%20in%20a%20way%20that%20America%20is%20trying%20to%20live%20up%20to%20our%20founding%20ideals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692193728000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16191110%2FF3pdtOWWkAAt5l9.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmeeting-between-us-delegation-rahul-gandhi-unlikely%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Congressperson%20Ro%20Khanna%20said%20that%20the%20delegation's%20meetings%20were%20subject%20to%20clearance%20from%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20ministry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmeeting-between-us-delegation-rahul-gandhi-unlikely%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Probe%20Agency%20Challenges%20Pre-Arrest%20Bail%20To%20Robert%20Vadra%20In%20Corruption%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20today%20challenged%20the%20anticipatory%20bail%20granted%20to%20Robert%20Vadra%2C%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20claiming%20non-compliance%20with%20bail%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20counsel%20said%20he%20will%20file%20an%20additional%20affidavit%20showing%20breach%20of%20bail%20conditions%20by%20Robert%20Vadra%20and%20sought%20some%20time%20to%20place%20it%20before%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sudhir%20Kumar%20Jain%20granted%20the%20ED%20two%20weeks%20to%20file%20the%20additional%20affidavit%20and%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20earlier%20told%20the%20high%20court%20it%20wanted%20to%20interrogate%20Robert%20Vadra%20in%20custody%2C%20alleging%20the%20%26quot%3Bmoney%20chain%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case%20was%20directly%20linked%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20also%20claimed%20he%20was%20not%20cooperating%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20Vadra%20is%20facing%20allegations%20of%20money%20laundering%20in%20the%20purchase%20of%20a%20property%20in%20London%20at%2012%2C%20Bryanston%20Square%2C%20estimated%20at%201.9%20million%20pounds%20(over%20Rs%2017%20crore).%20The%20case%20is%20being%20probed%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20Vadra's%20lawyer%20had%20rejected%20the%20ED's%20allegations%20and%20said%20his%20client%20cooperated%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20appeared%20before%20the%20probe%20agency%20whenever%20summoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20was%20hearing%20the%20ED's%20plea%20challenging%20the%20anticipatory%20bail%20granted%20to%20Robert%20Vadra%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20on%20April%201%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20Vadra%20had%20opposed%20the%20plea%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20not%20even%20a%20single%20instance%20of%20his%20non-cooperation.%20He%20said%20there%20was%20no%20risk%20of%20him%20tampering%20with%20evidence%20as%20the%20agency%20has%20already%20seized%20from%20him%20every%20document%20pertaining%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20was%20conducting%20a%20%26quot%3Bfishing%20and%20roving%20enquiry%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20no%20material%20to%20support%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20him%2C%20he%20had%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20agency's%20claim%20that%20he%20was%20a%20flight%20risk%2C%20Robert%20Vadra%20had%20said%20in%20his%20reply%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20conduct%20of%20the%20respondent%20(Robert%20Vadra)%20in%20returning%20to%20India%20from%20abroad%20voluntarily%20upon%20reading%20press%20reports%20that%20ED%20was%20investigating%20him%20made%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20Robert%20Vadra%20had%20no%20intention%20whatsoever%20of%20fleeing%20the%20country%20and%20was%20determined%20to%20stay%20in%20India%20and%20clear%20the%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20granting%20anticipatory%20bail%20to%20Robert%20Vadra%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20had%20directed%20him%20not%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20without%20prior%20permission%20and%20also%20to%20join%20the%20probe%20as%20and%20when%20called%20by%20the%20investigating%20officer.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692193560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Fj0j5rhn8_robert-vadra-ndtv-650_650x400_06_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http