202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeavy%20rain%20continues%20to%20wreak%20havoc%20in%20multiple%20areas%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20causing%20widespread%20damage%20to%20buildings%20and%20properties%2C%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20schools%20and%20colleges%20across%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20will%20remain%20closed%20till%20August%2019%20in%20view%20of%20the%20extreme%20weather%2C%20NDTV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F60-dead-himachal-sees-more-landslides-heavy-rain-alert-4301732%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20neighbouring%20Uttarakhand%2C%20The%20Dehradun%20Met%20department%20has%20predicted%20light%20to%20moderate%20rain%20accompanied%20by%20thunderstorms%20at%20Nainital%2C%20Champawat%20and%20Udham%20Singh%20Nagar%20districts%2C%20at%20many%20places%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20Tehri%2C%20Pauri%20and%20Almora%20districts%20and%20at%20a%20few%20places%20in%20the%20remaining%20districts%20of%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NDTV%20report%2C%20officials%20said%20at%20least%20800%20roads%20are%20blocked%20in%20the%20state%20due%20to%20landslides%20and%20the%20state%20has%20suffered%20losses%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20this%20monsoon%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20has%20said%20his%20state%20would%20take%20a%20year%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20damage%20incurred%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20season%20and%20the%20estimated%20loss%20in%20the%20two%20devastating%20spells%20of%20heavy%20rain%20%E2%80%93%20this%20week%20and%20in%20July%20%E2%80%93%20is%20about%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%2C%20NDTV%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20have%20witnessed%20dozens%20of%20deaths%20this%20monsoon%20and%20are%20set%20to%20receive%20more%20rain%2C%20according%20to%20weather%20forecasts%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20declare%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20a%20disaster-hit%20state%2C%20NDTV%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692189741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16180657%2Fcc4e44da-c1e7-4940-ad70-14a9cb35e957.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fhimachal-pradesh-another-landslide-in-shimla-death-toll-climbs-to-60%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20search%20and%20rescue%20operation%20was%20initiated%20with%20sniffer%20dogs%20and%20rescue%20personnel%20present%20at%20the%20site.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fhimachal-pradesh-another-landslide-in-shimla-death-toll-climbs-to-60%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Unholy%20Omen%20Is%20Looming%20Over%20Bangladesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F22151832%2FScreen-Shot-2021-10-22-at-3.17.47-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20a%20warm%20August%20night%2075%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20sun%20set%20on%20the%20British%20Raj.%20In%20the%20mottled%20dawn%20that%20followed%20came%20into%20existence%20two%2C%20then%20three%2C%20countries.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20country%20and%20provinces%20that%20were%20divided%20%E2%80%93%20to%20use%20Annada%20Shankar%20Ray%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20Partition%20entailed%20allotting%20everything%20from%20tea%20gardens%2C%20coal%20mines%2C%20colleges%2C%20police%20stations%2C%20office%20rooms%20to%20chairs%2C%20tables%2C%20wall%20clocks%20to%20peons%2C%20policemen%2C%20and%20professors%20into%20two%20countries.%C2%A0And%20it%20was%20accompanied%20by%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20population%20movements%20in%20human%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20seminal%202008%20article%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprbharadwaj.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPrashant%20Bharadwaj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20his%20colleagues%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdss.ucsd.edu%2F~prbharadwaj%2Findex%2FPapers_files%2FBharadwaj_Migration_EPW.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Big%20March%3A%20Migratory%20Flows%20after%20the%20Partition%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%20nearly%203%20million%20Hindus%20emigrated%20out%20of%20then%20East%20Pakistan%2C%20while%20three%20quarters%20of%20a%20million%20Muslims%20moved%20there%20from%20India.%20The%20relatively%20small%20number%20of%20people%20emigrating%20eastwards%2C%20juxtaposed%20against%20the%20relatively%20large%20number%20of%20people%20fleeing%2C%20possibly%20explains%20why%20the%20public%20memory%20of%20partition%20differs%20so%20starkly%20on%20the%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20Radcliffe%20Line%20in%20the%20eastern%20subcontinent.%20In%20Indian%20Bengal%2C%20partition%20is%20ever-present%20in%20the%20literature%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20visual%20media%2C%20in%20classic%20novels%20and%20movies%2C%20evoking%20a%20lost%20world%20and%20the%20plight%20of%20a%20people%20cut%20off%20from%20their%20rural%20roots%2C%20and%20their%20struggles%20among%20the%20teeming%20multitudes%20of%20Calcutta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20about%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20who%20stayed%20behind%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENirad%20C.%20Chaudhuri%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FJatin_Sarker%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJatin%20Sarker%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0were%20both%20born%20in%20Hindu%20families%20in%20the%20Mymensingh%20district%20of%20eastern%20Bengal%2C%20now%20Bangladesh.%20Chaudhuri%2C%20about%20four%20decades%20older%20than%20Sarkar%2C%20wrote%20his%20autobiography%20before%20India%20held%20its%20first%20election%2C%20and%20ceased%20to%20be%20unknown.%20Sarker%20also%20wrote%20his%20life%20story.%20Unlike%20Chaudhuri%2C%20Sarker%E2%80%99s%20was%20in%20Bangla%2C%20published%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20never%20translated%20in%20English%2C%20and%20not%20widely%20available.%20He%20remains%20unknown.%C2%A0Which%20is%20a%20pity%2C%20because%20Sarker%20is%20a%20far%2C%20far%20better%20guide%20than%20Chaudhuri%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20land%20of%20their%20birth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Sarker%E2%80%99s%20hometown%20Mymensingh%20became%20part%20of%20East%20Pakistan%20%E2%80%93%20the%20rural%20slum%20of%20Jinnah%E2%80%99s%20moth-nibbled%20two-winged%20land%20of%20the%20pure%20%E2%80%93%20his%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20move%20to%20India.%20They%20were%20not%20atypical.%20Many%20Hindu%20families%20remained%20in%20East%20Pakistan.%20Perhaps%20it%20was%20the%20presence%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20or%20the%20fantastical%20belief%20that%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20would%20return%20in%201957%20%E2%80%93%20a%20century%20after%20the%20Great%20Uprising%20of%201857%2C%20two%20centuries%20after%20the%20Battle%20of%20Plassey%20%E2%80%93%20to%20reunite%20Mother%20Bengal.%20Whatever%20the%20reason%2C%20there%20were%20no%20trains%20full%20of%20dead%20bodies%20to%20and%20from%20Calcutta%20in%20that%20dreadful%20August.%20Instead%2C%20there%20were%20emigrations%20in%20dribs%20and%20drabs%2C%20with%20major%20outflows%20during%20the%20communal%20violence%20of%201946%2C%201950%2C%20and%201964.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia-bangladesh-democracy-economy-sheikh-hasina%5C%22%3EWhy%20India%20Needs%20To%20Support%20the%20Quest%20for%20Restoring%20Democracy%20in%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarker%20describes%20the%20lives%20of%20middle%20class%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhadralok%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(gentlemen)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Hindus%20of%20mofussil%20East%20Pakistan%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPakistan-er%20Janma%20Mrittu%20Darshan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0(%E2%80%98Witnessing%20the%20Life%20and%20Death%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99).%C2%A0While%20he%20stopped%20being%20an%20Indian%20on%2014%20August%201947%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20become%20a%20Pakistani.%20That%20country%20became%20an%20Islamic%20Republic.%20Hindus%20were%20not%20equal%20citizens%20there.%20They%20were%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edhimmis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98sacred%20protection%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20majority.%20Sarker%20could%20never%20be%20a%20Pakistani%2C%20but%20his%20Bengali%20Muslim%20neighbours%20did%20not%20quite%20feel%20at%20home%20in%20Pakistan%20either.%20In%201971%2C%20when%20East%20Pakistan%20died%20and%20Bangladesh%20was%20born%2C%20Sarker%20thought%20he%20would%20become%20an%20equal%20citizen%20of%20a%20free%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20on%20paper%2C%20he%20is.%20Bangladesh%20never%20became%20an%20Islamic%20Republic%2C%20although%20Hussein%20Muhammad%20Ershad%2C%20military%20ruler%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20inserted%20Islam%20as%20the%20state%20religion%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20his%20ally%20andcurrent%20prime%20minister%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20refused%20to%20take%20it%20out%20despite%20other%20wholesale%20changes%20to%20the%20document.%20There%20is%20no%20formal%20discrimination%20with%20respect%20to%20religion.%20Hindus%20are%20not%20formally%20denied%20a%20job%2C%20a%20bank%20loan%2C%20or%20admission%20to%20an%20educational%20institution%20(except%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emadrassas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20course).%20On%20paper%2C%20Sarker%20has%20no%20reason%20to%20write%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBangladeshey%20Pakistan-er%20bhut%20darshan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0(%E2%80%98Witnessing%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Ghost%20in%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99)%2C%20a%20hypothetical%20sequel%20where%20he%20might%20have%20talked%20about%20things%20that%20one%20did%20not%20wish%20for%20in%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20of%20Bangladesh.Things%20like%20communal%20violence%20targeting%20Hindus%20for%20example.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20communal%20violence%2C%20one%20does%20not%20mean%20a%20Gujrat%202002%20%E2%80%93%20nothing%20like%20that%20has%20ever%20happened%20in%20Bangladesh.%20And%20one%20also%20needs%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20mutual%20apathy%20and%20distrust%2C%20if%20not%20overt%20antagonism%2C%20between%20the%20eastern%20subcontinent%E2%80%99s%20two%20large%20religious%20communities%20(and%20multiple%20ethnic%20communities)%20is%20much%20more%20complex%20than%20the%20tales%20of%20eternal%20harmony.%20As%20Annada%20Shankar%20Ray%20noted%2C%20the%20two%20communities%20had%20co-existed%20in%20the%20region%20for%20generations%20and%20centuries%20without%20really%20intermingling.%20Of%20course%2C%20that%20complex%20interplay%20of%20historical%20legacy%20affects%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20interpersonal%20interactions%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20%E2%80%94no%20one%20is%20better%20off%20to%20deny%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20a%20fascinating%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0167268117303384%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexperiment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Pushkar%20Maitra%20and%20colleagues%20show%20that%20it%20is%20the%20minority%20status%2C%20not%20religious%20identity%20itself%2C%20that%20drives%20people%E2%80%99s%20behaviour.%20That%20is%2C%20a%20Muslim%20in%20West%20Bengal%20trusts%20a%20fellow%20Muslim%20more%20than%20a%20Hindu%2C%20but%20a%20Bangladeshi%20Muslim%20is%20indifferent%20between%20the%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20historical%20legacy%20of%20the%20divergent%20paths%20taken%20by%20the%20two%20communities%20in%20the%2018th%20and%2019th%20century%20continue%20to%20have%20economic%20consequences%20even%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20Bangladesh.%20Salma%20Ahmed%20found%20that%20even%20in%20the%20decade%20to%202009%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fideas.repec.org%2Fp%2Fpra%2Fmprapa%2F75153.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20male%20workers%20earnt%20more%20than%20their%20Muslim%20colleagues%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20because%20they%20were%20better%20educated%20on%20average%2C%20but%20they%20faced%20discrimination%20and%20earnt%20less%20than%20might%20have%20been%20expected%20from%20their%20qualification.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20no%20law%20supporting%20discrimination%20against%20Hindus.%20There%20is%2C%20however%2C%20a%20law%20that%20makes%20the%20community%20particularly%20vulnerable%20%E2%80%94%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.askbd.org%2Fhr_report2008%2F15_Religious.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EEnemy%20Property%20Act%201965%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20its%20Bangladeshi%20successors%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Act%20allows%20the%20state%20to%20seize%20properties%20of%20those%20who%20leave%20the%20country.%20In%20practice%2C%20this%20has%20been%20used%20over%20the%20decades%20to%20grab%20Hindu%20properties.%20Typically%2C%20local%20big-wigs%20grab%20some%20prime%20land%2C%20and%20then%20use%20death%20or%20emigration%20of%20one%20of%20the%20family%20members%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20enlist%20the%20entire%20property.%20If%20emigration%20is%20not%20voluntary%2C%20coercion%20or%20intimidation%20is%20commonplace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Abul%20Barakat%2C%20as%20of%202000%2C%20over%20two-fifths%20of%20Hindu%20households%20had%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20Act%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20over%20half%20of%20their%20land%20(over%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20land%20area%20of%20Bangladesh).%20This%20transfer%20of%20land%2C%20however%2C%20benefitted%20less%20than%200.4%25%20of%20Bangladeshis.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20land%20reform%20by%20the%20state%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20downtrodden.%20The%20beneficiaries%20were%20those%20with%20the%20might%20that%20comes%20from%20political%20connections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20were%20the%20political%20affiliations%20of%20the%20offenders%3F%20According%20to%20Barakat%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20well-connected%20with%20the%20Awami%20League%2C%20allegedly%20contributing%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20platform%20in%20the%202000s%20and%20rewarded%20with%20cushy%20jobs%20by%20the%20current%20government%20%E2%80%93%20over%2044%25%20of%20the%20land%20grabbers%20were%20connected%20with%20the%20Awami%20League%2C%20more%20than%20the%20combined%20total%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%2C%20Jatiya%20Party%20and%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20linked%20offenders.%20And%20this%20study%20came%20out%20in%202000%2C%20well%20before%20the%20current%2015%20years%20of%20Awami%20League%20reign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20thus%20we%20come%20to%20the%20dysfunctional%20polity%20that%20curses%20the%20life%20of%20Bangladeshi%20Hindus.%20All%20the%20historical%20legacies%20notwithstanding%2C%20the%20single%20biggest%20threat%20to%20the%20wellbeing%20of%20Bangladeshi%20Hindus%20in%202023%20is%20an%20authoritarian%20and%20increasingly%20dysfunctional%20political%20landscape%20where%20most%20members%20of%20the%20community%20are%20treated%20as%20the%20expendable%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Euntermensch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(racially%20or%20socially%20inferior)%20by%20the%20powers-that-be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20there%20has%20been%20no%20incident%20comparable%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20there%20has%20been%20violence.%20In%20December%201992%2C%20when%20the%20centuries-old%20Babri%20mosque%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20razed%20to%20ground%2C%20temples%20were%20desecrated%20across%20Bangladesh.%20Khaleda%20Zia%2C%20then%20prime%20minister%2C%20ordered%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20move%20in%20quickly%20to%20stem%20the%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZia%20must%20have%20remembered%20the%20experience%20very%20well.%20The%20Gujarat%20rampage%20happened%20during%20her%20second%20stint%20in%20power.%20Her%20government%20ensured%20that%20there%20were%20no%20reprisals%20against%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Bangladesh.%20She%20was%20also%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20communal%20violence%20that%20marred%20her%20return%20to%20power%20in%202001.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%20300%20seats%20in%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20parliament%2C%20Hindus%20were%20a%20non-trivial%20minority%20in%20about%2070.%20In%20a%20tight%20election%2C%20their%20votes%20could%20make%20a%20huge%20difference.%20Not%20allowing%20them%20to%20vote%20was%20one%20way%20of%20reducing%20their%20influence.%C2%A0That%20is%20precisely%20what%20happened%20in%202001.%20In%20that%20election%2C%20Awami%20League%20received%2040%25%20of%20the%20votes%20against%20the%20BNP%E2%80%99s%2041%25.%20Hindu%20voters%20in%20some%20districts%20became%20the%20victim%20of%20targeted%20communal%20violence%20after%20the%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBangladesh%E2%80%99s%20stressed%20and%20stretched%20electoral%20democracy%20failed%20to%20safeguard%20the%20Hindu%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20story%2C%20of%20course%2C%20does%20not%20end%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20decades%20later%2C%20images%20and%20stories%20of%20the%20victims%20of%202001%20resurfaced%20in%20a%20toxic%20cocktail%20of%20misinformation%20and%20propaganda%20against%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjrahman.substack.com%2Fp%2Fkhela-hobe%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%202021%20West%20Bengal%20election%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Majoritarian%20democracy%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20safeguard%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights%2C%20this%20much%20is%20self-evident%20when%20one%20looks%20across%20the%20Radcliffe%20Line.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20discarding%20democracy%20is%20guaranteed%20to%20extinguish%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights%2C%20this%20much%20is%20also%20self-evident%20when%20one%20just%20thinks%20of%20Bangladesh%20of%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bangladesh%20under%20a%20supposedly%20secular%2C%20inclusive%20government%20of%20Hasina%20Wajed%2C%20however%2C%20there%20has%20been%20repeated%20communal%20violence%2C%20with%20active%20connivance%20if%20not%20instigation%20of%20her%20partymen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENever%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20Hindu%20community%20saw%20coordinated%20attacks%20on%20temples%20during%20Durga%20Puja%2C%20until%202021%20that%20is%2C%20after%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Quran%20was%20found%20in%20a%20temple.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20spread%20like%20wildfire%20and%20soon%2C%20angry%20mobs%20started%20attacking%20temples%20across%20the%20country.%20Within%20four%20days%2C%20eight%20people%20died%20including%20three%20Hindus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20coordinated%20attack%2C%20in%20Chandpur%2C%20Ariyan%20Sajjad%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%E2%80%99s%20student%20wing%20and%20son%20of%20local%20Awami%20League%20leader%20Shahida%20Begum%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fnews%2Fbangladesh%2Fcrime-justice%2Fnews%2Fpattern-always-the-same-2202321%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%20the%20local%20Muslims%20to%20launch%20an%20attack%20on%20temples%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epandals%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Hindus%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdesecration%20of%20Quran%E2%80%9D%20.%20In%20Bandarban%2C%20Awami%20League%20leader%20Zahirul%20Islam%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fnews%2Fbangladesh%2Fnews%2Ffriends-became-strangers-the-blink-eye-2199336%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaddressed%20the%20mob%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20before%20they%20started%20attacking%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident.%20As%20a%20former%20officer%20of%20the%20Indian%20Police%20Service%2C%20Vibhuti%20Rai%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Famp%2Fstory%2Fopinion%252Fmanipur-silence-of-consent-will-destroy-the-indian-state-1237395.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eremarked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20communal%20violence%20in%20India%2C%20no%20such%20event%20can%20last%20for%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20a%20sentiment%20that%20is%20applicable%20on%20an%20even%20shorter%20time-frame%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20given%20the%20more%20compressed%20distances%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAin%20O%20Salish%20Kendra%2C%20a%20Bangladeshi%20human%20rights%20organisation%2C%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbdnews24.com%2Fbangladesh%2Fwith-3679-attacks-in-9-years-bangladeshs-hindus-at-regular-threat-of-violence-ask%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edocumented%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%203%2C679%20incidents%20of%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20from%202013%20to%202021%2C%20which%20included%201%2C559%20incidents%20of%20housebreaking%20and%20arson%2C%201%2C678%20incidents%20of%20vandalism%20and%20arson%20in%20idols%2C%20worship%20halls%2C%20and%20temples%20and%20the%20death%20of%2011%20Hindus%20in%20these%20attacks%20.%20The%20individuals%20involved%20in%20these%20attacks%20are%20loyal%20to%20Awami%20League%2C%20Bangladeshi%20media%20outlets%20revealed.%20For%20example%2C%20people%20close%20to%20Shamsul%20Hoque%20Tuku%2C%20the%20deputy%20speaker%20of%20parliament%2C%20perpetrated%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fnews%2Fsome-attackers-seen-with-tuku%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etargeted%20violence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20Hindu%20village%20in%20Pabna%20.%20Dozens%20of%20Hindu%20houses%20and%20business%20establishments%20in%20Brahmanbaria%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Ffrontpage%2Fattack-hindus-brahmanbaria-ambition-not-religion-1327456%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eattacked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20followers%20of%20Obaidul%20Muktadir%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20local%20member%20of%20parliament%20and%20a%20former%20personal%20aide%20to%20Hasina%2C%20in%202016%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20none%20of%20the%20cases%20involving%20the%20attacks%20on%20minority%20communities%20have%20been%20properly%20investigated.%20This%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20Bangladesh%20has%20been%20under%20a%20de%20facto%20one-party%2C%20if%20not%20one-person%2C%20rule%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20now.%20Hasina%20Wajed%E2%80%99s%20authoritarian%20regime%20may%20or%20may%20not%20come%20to%20an%20end%20soon%20%E2%80%93%20elections%20are%20due%20in%20a%20few%20months%20and%20discontent%20is%20risingbut%20then%20again%2C%20she%20rigged%20the%20last%20two%20and%20may%20as%20well%20rig%20another%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20every%20reason%20to%20fear%20that%20the%20increasingly%20beleaguered%20dictator%20may%20turn%20to%20the%20age-old%20tactic%20of%20communal%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%201990%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%20led%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20across%20India%20to%20demand%20the%20razing%20of%20the%20Babri%20mosque.%20In%20Dhaka%2C%20goons%20associated%20with%20his%20party%20vandalised%20the%20Dhakeshwari%20Temple%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20to%20give%20President%20Ershad%20an%20excuse%20to%20impose%20curfew%20and%20act%20like%20a%20statesman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EErshad%E2%80%99s%20gambit%20failed%2C%20and%20his%20government%20fell%20the%20next%20month%20after%20a%20popular%20uprising.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMight%20Hasina%20update%20the%20playbook%20for%20the%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20deploying%20social%20media%20and%20disinformation%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20a%20far%20more%20draconian%20state%20machinery%20of%20repression%20on%20the%20other%2C%20all%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20Hindutva%20government%20seeking%20a%20third%20term%20in%20India%20a%20few%20months%20later%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20does%20not%20need%20to%20be%20a%20paranoid%20conspiracy%20monger%20to%20be%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20unholy%20omen%20as%20we%20approach%20the%20autumn%20%E2%80%93%20the%20traditional%20festive%20season%20of%20the%20Bengali%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENearly%2076%20years%20after%20partition%2C%20Gayeshwar%20Chandra%20Roy%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BNP%20standing%20committee%2C%20recently%20bemoaned%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20sad%20fact%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20minority%20community%20have%20no%20say%20anywhere%3B%20neitherr%20in%20administration%2C%20nor%20in%20judiciary.%20In%20one%20word%2C%20Bangladesh%20does%20not%20care.%20Due%20to%20insecurity%2C%20there%20is%20a%20gradual%20exodus%20of%20Hindus%20from%20Bangladesh.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%2077%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Bengal%20delta%20was%20red%20with%20communal%20bloodletting%20that%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20stopped%20by%20the%20British%20Raj%20in%20its%20last%20days%2C%20until%20a%20frail%20old%20man%20came%20with%20a%20message%20of%20peace.%20There%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20no%20Mahatma%20in%20Bangladesh.%20But%20nor%20is%20one%20needed.%20It%20would%20suffice%20for%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20do%20what%20it%20did%20in%201992%20or%202002.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reality%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20Bangladeshi%20state%20has%20become%20very%20good%20at%20stamping%20out%20dissent.%20But%20given%20the%20rot%2C%20it%20has%20become%20very%20bad%20at%20statehood%20and%20the%20type%20of%20resolute%20action%20that%20would%20have%20thwarted%20these%20attacks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20and%20unless%20there%20is%20an%20honest%20acknowledgment%20that%20the%20state%20is%20broken%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20rebuilt%2C%20with%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20as%20the%20first%20step%20of%20that%20process%2C%20Bangladesh%20will%20remain%20haunted%20by%20the%20spectre%20of%20unholy%20omens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EJyoti%20Rahman%20is%20a%20Bangladeshi%20writer.%20His%20pieces%20are%20archived%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjrahman.substack.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fjrahman.substack.com%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20title%20of%20this%20piece%20refers%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAshani%20Sanket%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20classic%20Bangla%20novel%20by%20Bibhuti%20Bhushan%20Bandopadyaya%2C%20filmed%20by%20Satyajit%20Ray%20in%201973.%20The%20English%20title%20of%20the%20movie%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EDistant%C2%A0Thunder%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20the%20literal%20translation%20of%20the%20Bangla%20title%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20Unholy%20Omen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692189044000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F22151832%2FScreen-Shot-2021-10-22-at-3.17.47-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fan-unholy-omen-is-looming-over-bangladesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20every%20reason%20to%20fear%20that%20Bangladesh%20may%20witness%20the%20age-old%20tactic%20of%20communal%20violence%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20election.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fan-unholy-omen-is-looming-over-bangladesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actors%20who%20survived%20on%20their%20wives'%20earnings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692189000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102775092%2Cimgsize-60712.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-pankaj-tripathi-ayushmann-khurrana-b-town-actors-who-confessed-to-have-survived-on-their-wives-earnings%2Fphotostory%2F102775092.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102775092.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%2C%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%3A%20B-Town%20actors%20who%20confessed%20to%20have%20survived%20on%20their%20wives'%20earnings%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-pankaj-tripathi-ayushmann-khurrana-b-town-actors-who-confessed-to-have-survived-on-their-wives-earnings%2Fphotostory%2F102775092.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3