inal-after-win-over-hosts-australia-12941063%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fenglands-lionesses-through-to-their-first-world-cup-final-after-win-over-hosts-australia-12941063%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Is%20a%20Test%20Bed%20of%20New%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095357%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.01-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20threw%20up%20two%20diverse%20view%20points%20on%20the%20utility%20of%20force%20in%20internal%20security%20situations.%20While%20either%20option%20%E2%80%93%20use%20and%20non-use%20%E2%80%93%20can%20reasonably%20be%20adopted%20by%20a%20government%20in%20such%20circumstance%2C%20what%20intrigues%20is%20justification%20in%20Parliament%20for%20the%20non-use%20of%20force%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3Ehis%20intervention%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20in%20parliament%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20profiting%20from%20the%20uncanny%20timing%20of%20reinsertion%20into%20the%20parliament%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMIj9l7MsFtU%5C%22%3Eobserved%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Manipur%20need%20not%20have%20spiralled%20into%20violence%20had%20the%20Army%20been%20employed%20in%20time.%20With%20the%20Army%20in%20place%2C%20the%20violent%20political%20extremism%20witnessed%20there%20could%20have%20been%20nipped%20in%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20response%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20his%20government%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20appeared%20wary%20of%20the%20use%20of%20force%20to%20address%20such%20situations.%20He%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20Mizoram%2C%20wherein%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DguGPYNQjjYM%5C%22%3Eto%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20then%20government%20was%20guilty%20of%20targeting%20innocent%20civilians%20with%20the%20employment%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF).%20For%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20added%20the%20example%20of%20the%20assault%20on%20Akal%20Takht.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%20in%20a%20meet%20with%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrnDcCx98K2o%5C%22%3Epress%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reply%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20two-hour-plus-long%20speech%20in%20parliament%2C%20Gandhi%20clarified%20that%20Army%20deployment%20is%20one%20among%20many%20instruments%20the%20government%20has%2C%20which%20when%20deployed%20complementarily%20can%20control%20civil%20unrest%20in%20two-three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20%E2%80%93%20b%C3%AAte%20noire%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20and%20resident%20expert%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20regime%20on%20the%20North%20East%20%E2%80%93%20was%20quick%20to%20attack%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20take.%20He%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvnlsJhPbqxI%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20military%20would%20have%20served%20no%20purpose%20in%20the%20circumstance.%20Citing%20the%20Mizoram%20episode%2C%20he%20rhetorically%20queried%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20(the%20Army)%20should%20open%20fire%20on%20civilians%3F%20Is%20it%20his%20prescription%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20rather%20obvious%20that%20both%20Modi%20and%20Sarma%20have%20a%20coloured%20notion%20of%20the%20use%20of%20the%20IAF%20in%20Mizoram.%20For%20their%20political%20purpose%20of%20beating%20back%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20charge%2C%20they%20have%20twisted%20the%20unfortunate%20deaths%20of%20civilians%20in%20the%20bombing%20by%20the%20IAF%20of%20Aizawl%20back%20in%201966%20as%20deliberate%20targeting%20of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20backlash%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20take%20on%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20operations%20in%20Mizoram%20is%20amply%20clear%20that%20the%20IAF%20close%20air%20support%20operations%20in%20Aizawl%20were%20undertaken%20in%20the%20extreme%20conditions%20of%20an%20attempted%20take-over%20of%20the%20then%20Mizo%20Hills%20District%20of%20Assam%20by%20the%20separatist%2C%20Pakistan-supported%20militant%20group%2C%20Mizo%20National%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20operated%20in%20support%20of%20the%20beleaguered%20garrisons%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%20Given%20the%20technology%20of%20the%20times%2C%20undeniably%20there%20were%20some%20civilian%20deaths.%20Though%20regrettable%2C%20should%20the%20risk%20have%20led%20to%20dropping%20of%20the%20option%20altogether%3F%20That%20it%20yet%20required%20brigade-level%20land%20operations%20lasting%20almost%20a%20month%20to%20dislodge%20the%20insurgents%20shows%20the%20constraints%20India%20and%20the%20military%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20emerges%20that%20in%20a%20consideration%20of%20factors%20involved%2C%20including%20collateral%20damage%2C%20a%20judicious%20decision%20has%20to%20be%20arrived%20at%20the%20political%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisconstruing%20the%20aim%20of%20the%20operations%20%E2%80%93%20that%20civilians%20were%20targets%20%E2%80%93%20shows%20up%20a%20political%20motive.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20lying%20in%20parliament%20must%20be%20appraised%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20obvious%20strand%20of%20the%20politics%20is%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20less%20obvious%20one%20also%20merits%20a%20look%3A%20coup-proofing.%20More%20on%20the%20second%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20before%20addressing%20the%20politics%20is%20a%20look%20at%20use%20of%20force%20decision%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20use%20of%20force%20in%20internal%20security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outbreak%20in%20early%20May%20of%20the%20internal%20security%20situation%20that%20persists%20till%20today%20witnessed%20brazen%20looting%20of%20arms%20from%20police%20premises%20and%20their%20subsequent%20use%20by%20ethnic%20militias%20for%20perpetrating%20what%20amount%20to%20crimes%20against%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20gainsaying%20that%20both%20internal%20security%20situations%20%E2%80%93%20Mizoram%20and%20Punjab%20%E2%80%93%20were%20preventable.%20To%20argue%20however%20that%20military%20force%20should%20have%20been%20ruled%20out%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20crunch%20in%20both%20places%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20civilians%20got%20killed%20%E2%80%93%20is%20debatable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Golden%20Temple%2C%20the%20use%20of%20military%20force%20is%20easier%20to%20justify%20in%20retrospect%20since%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20the%20complex%20had%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20veritable%20fortress.%20It%20required%20extensive%20firing%20of%20the%20formidable%20main%20gun%20of%20tanks%20to%20dislodge%20its%20terrorist%20defenders%2C%20a%20decision%20taken%20after%20a%20rather%20steep%20price%20paid%20in%20lives%20of%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mizoram%2C%20when%20trouble%20broke%20out%2C%20the%20closest%20brigade%20headquarters%20was%20at%20Agartala.%20The%20forces%20to%20do%20the%20job%20of%20vacating%20the%20MNF%20threat%20required%20first%20being%20concentrated%20and%20then%20inducted.%20This%20would%20give%20the%20militants%20sufficient%20time%20to%20consolidate%20their%20gains%20in%20Aizawl%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20making%20deliberate%20operations%20with%20a%20larger%20force%20inescapable%2C%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20higher%20toll%20in%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Sarma%20is%20right%20that%20the%20employment%20of%20the%20Army%20does%20not%20resolve%20anything%20and%20can%20only%20quieten%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20precisely%20the%20intent.%20Army%20doctrine%20has%20it%20that%20its%20deployment%20is%20to%20reduce%20violence%20to%20levels%20even%20as%20political%20processes%20kick-in%20to%20resolve%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20also%20quick%20to%20clarify%20at%20his%20press%20meet%20that%20he%20meant%20resort%20to%20military%20force%20is%20an%20option%20that%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20and%20is%20only%20part%20of%20a%20package%20of%20measures%20taken%20with%20the%20instruments%20of%20State%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20the%20two%20politicians%20appear%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicability%20of%20force%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20judgment.%20The%20risk%20of%20civilian%20casualties%20must%20be%20factored%20in%20and%20the%20level%20of%20risk%20can%20serve%20to%20stall%20or%20moderate%20military%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20this%20conclusion%20square%20with%20the%20situations%20that%20sequentially%20obtained%20in%20Manipur%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20truism%20in%20theory%20on%20controlling%20of%20internal%20security%20situations%20is%20that%20inter-community%20fights%20can%20be%20controlled%20within%2048%20hours%2C%20in%20case%20of%20political%20will%20and%20a%20clear%20mandate%20to%20the%20police.%20The%20Army%20must%20be%20called%20in%20timely%20in%20aid%20to%20civil%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20it%20was%20very%20much%20possible%20for%20the%20state%20government%20to%20firmly%20deal%20with%20the%20mobs%20using%20the%20police%20and%20central%20police%20forces%20at%20hand%20and%20call%20for%20Army%20deployment%20as%20necessary.%20Such%20demonstration%20of%20resolve%20on%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98double-engine%E2%80%99%20government%20could%20have%20prevented%20conflict%20spiral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20force%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20causing%20loss%20of%20life%20%E2%80%93%20may%20have%20been%20inescapable.%20The%20argument%20that%20civilians%20would%20have%20been%20killed%20seems%20to%20view%20participants%20in%20mobs%20as%20%E2%80%98innocent%20civilians%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20not%20the%20case%20when%20such%20mobs%20are%20raiding%20sensitive%20government%20premises%20with%20nefarious%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circumstance%20was%20in%20no%20way%20reminiscent%20of%20instances%20of%20use%20of%20force%20against%20civilians%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20as%20at%20Gow%20Kadal%2C%20on%20the%20Mirwaiz%20funeral%20procession%20and%20at%20Bijbehara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiring%20is%20under%20rules%20of%20engagement%20that%20compel%20proportionality%20and%20discrimination.%20The%20upshot%20is%20deterrence%2C%20preventing%20widespread%20unrest%20and%20resort%20to%20higher%20degrees%20of%20force.%20Therefore%2C%20though%20regrettable%20in%20every%20instance%2C%20any%20innocent%20lives%20lost%20must%20be%20seen%20in%20relation%20to%20good%20faith%20in%20conduct%20and%20expected%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reading%20makes%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20questioning%20of%20the%20response%20to%20the%20outbreak%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20consider%20whether%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20greater%20government%20resolve%20would%20have%20ended%20the%20largely%20tit-for-tat%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%2C%20assisting%20the%20police%20and%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%2C%20would%20have%20had%20to%20contend%20with%20well%20armed%20militias.%20Forcible%20disarmament%20therefore%20recedes%20in%20priority%20as%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Army%20could%20have%20proven%20more%20efficacious%20than%20CAPF%20alone%20in%20securing%20people%20in%20situ.%20The%20CAPF%20are%20held%20hostage%20to%20the%20police%2C%20which%20in%20Manipur%20was%20partisan.%20There%20is%20no%20ethic%20of%20independent%20professional%20action%20in%20the%20CAPF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%E2%80%99s%20availability%20would%20have%20resulted%20in%20credibility%20for%20any%20governmental%20thrust%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20The%20ruling%20party%2C%20that%20has%20members%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20from%20both%20sides%2C%20was%20well%20positioned%20to%20bring%20about%20such%20a%20draw-down.%20The%20double%20engine%20holds%20a%20promise%20that%20both%20communities%20might%20like%20to%20avail%20themselves%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20lesser%20engine%20proved%20parochial%2C%20which%20explains%20why%20the%20Army%20was%20not%20more%20in%20evidence%20as%20part%20of%20the%20solution%20in%20first%20place.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20less%20responsive%20to%20the%20state%20administration%2C%20as%20was%20proved%20in%20the%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20dismissing%20the%20lesser%20engine%E2%80%99s%20characterising%20of%20the%20situation%20as%20one%20resulting%20from%20an%20insurgency-drugs%20nexus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20indicates%20that%20stability%20is%20in%20the%20offing.%20It%E2%80%99s%20possible%20that%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20the%20%E2%80%98hurting%20stalemate%E2%80%99%20theory%20rather%20too%20seriously%20and%20is%20waiting%20for%20the%20two%20sides%20to%20exhaust%20their%20firepower%20and%20angst.%20The%20trouble%20with%20this%20theory%20is%20that%20in%20the%20interim%20fissures%20widen%2C%20ruling%20out%20easy%20or%20early%20reconciliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aspect%20worth%20reminding%20is%20the%20State%20must%20regain%20monopoly%20over%20violence%2C%20preferably%20in%20a%20politically%20brokered%20way%2C%20but%2C%20if%20necessary%20eventually%2C%20by%20use%20of%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20disarmament%20should%20not%20amount%20to%20a%20Jaffna%20redux.%20Recall%20at%20Jaffna%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Tigers%20has%20to%20be%20bearded%20in%20their%20own%20den%2C%20at%20a%20high%20cost%20in%20lives%20of%20Indian%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20more%20fraught%20in%20the%20Valley%2C%20since%20the%20lesser%20engine%20has%20a%20pronounced%20bias%20towards%20the%20majority%20community.%20Selective%20impunity%20based%20on%20ethnic%20affiliation%20is%20likely.%20Instead%2C%20it%20should%20use%20affinity%20to%20encourage%20self-regulated%20disarmament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20assumption%20that%20the%20militias%2C%20having%20tasted%20power%2C%20will%20comply%20meekly%20is%20misplaced.%20It%20is%20not%20impossible%20that%20the%20militias%20will%20not%20be%20messed%20with%2C%20the%20excuse%20being%20they%20are%20%E2%80%98our%20boys.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20implies%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20on%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20continuing%20relevance%20in%20internal%20security%20remains%20valid%20as%20Manipur%20wades%20into%20an%20uncertain%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMajoritarianism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lesser%20engine%E2%80%99s%20actions%20are%20self-confessedly%20informed%20by%20majoritarian%20thinking%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%20ethnic.%20The%20senior%20engine%20played%20along%2C%20since%20it%20is%20likewise%20imbued%20with%20majoritarian%20thinking%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%20case%2C%20cultural.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glue%20between%20the%20two%20is%20the%20appropriation%20of%20nativist%20turn%20in%20Manipur%20to%20its%20own%20ends%20by%20Hindutva.%20Symbiosis%20between%20the%20two%20majoritarian%20strands%20%E2%80%93%20one%20local%20and%20the%20other%20national%20%E2%80%93%20led%20to%20the%20backing%20by%20the%20senior%20of%20the%20local.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppeasement%20as%20a%20political%20strategy%20can%20be%20endorsed%20if%20capable%20of%20winning%20the%20day%2C%20but%20implementing%20it%20without%20covering%20the%20flanks%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20with%20the%20Army%20deployed%20as%20deterrent%20%E2%80%93%20is%20chimerical.%20The%20result%20is%20not%20political%20resolution%2C%20but%20political%20acquiescence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20excusable%20taking%20cue%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Do%20No%20Harm%E2%80%99%20principle.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20violence%20being%20largely%20one-sided%2C%20such%20posture%20tends%20to%20disfavour%20the%20victimised.%20This%20shows%20up%20the%20approach%20as%20instrumental.%20The%20grant%20of%20the%20impunity%20allows%20Hindutva%20to%20draw%20its%20local%20counterpart%20into%20a%20more%20intimate%20bear-hug.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvoidance%20of%20civilian%20casualties%20is%20an%20alibi.%20The%20lesser%20engine%20was%20selectively%20gung-ho%20after%20Kukis%2C%20even%20launching%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20against%20an%20Assam%20Rifles%20outfit%20for%20impeding%20operations%20against%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20can%20quibble%20over%20%E2%80%98civilian%E2%80%99%20status.%C2%A0%20Logically%20when%20engaged%20in%20raiding%20an%20armoury%20or%2C%20as%20members%20of%20a%20mob%20perpetrating%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20individuals%20lose%20their%20civilian%20status%20for%20the%20duration.%20When%20busy%20violating%20the%20law%20and%20humanity%2C%20they%20can%20be%20at%20the%20business%20end%20of%20the%20law%20enforcers%E2%80%99%20stick%2C%20with%20due%20regard%20to%20restraints%20on%20the%20use%20of%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20senior%20engine%20does%20not%20think%20so%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20Why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20is%20the%20new%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faliahd66.substack.com%2Fp%2Fmanipur-as-hindutva-laboratory%5C%22%3Elaboratory%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Were%20the%20two%20engines%20to%20intercept%20and%20intervene%20in%20concert%2C%20they%20would%20be%20acting%20against%20their%20very%20own%20foot-soldiers%20pursuing%20an%20agenda%20set%20by%20the%20two%20engines%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStyling%20these%20as%20%E2%80%98innocent%20people%E2%80%99%2C%20Modi%20seeks%20to%20justify%20mobocracy%20%E2%80%93%20for%20a%20second%20time.%20Recall%20the%2048%20hours%20given%20to%20malevolent%20mobs%20in%20Gujarat%20of%20late%20February%202002.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20expose%20this%20sleight%20of%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerversely%20interpreted%2C%20Command%20Responsibility%20requires%20that%20having%20put%20their%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eunauthorised%20forces%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20militias%20and%20mobs%20%E2%80%93%20to%20work%2C%20majoritarian%20masters%20cannot%20also%20simultaneously%20exercise%20Command%20Responsibility%20%E2%80%93%20rightly%20interpreted%20%E2%80%93%20over%20the%20%3Cem%3Eauthorised%20forces%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20their%20disposal%20to%20stop%20the%20proceedings%20they%20have%20themselves%20set%20unauthorised%20forces%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitias%20are%20Hindutva%E2%80%99s%20private%20army%2C%20meant%20to%20undercut%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20monopoly%20of%20force.%20The%20State%20as%20bystander%20allows%20for%20Hindutva%20to%20fashion%20India%20in%20its%20own%20image.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20sword%20arm%20needs%20first%20to%20be%20neutered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoup%20proofing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20up%20the%20second%20political%20factor%3A%20coup-proofing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20is%20the%20visible%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20soldier%20on%20a%20pedestal%2C%20such%20as%20through%20Parakram%20Parv%2C%20National%20War%20Memorial%2C%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%3B%20alongside%2C%20is%20the%20insidious%20hollowing%20out%20of%20the%20military%20as%20an%20institution%2C%20with%2C%20for%20example%2C%20deep%20selection%2C%20Agnipath%20and%20the%20decolonisation%20bogey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20%E2%80%93%20that%20identifies%20more%20with%20the%20Army%20and%20less%20with%20the%20ministry%20it%20is%20administratively%20under%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20on%20the%20cross-hairs%20of%20the%20lesser%20engine.%20Controversially%2C%20the%20lesser%20engine%20wanted%20to%20redeploy%20it%20away%20from%20a%20non-existent%20post!%20The%20Spear%20Corps%20has%20also%20had%20occasion%20to%20point%20out%20the%20manner%20an%20unarmed%20women-only%20militia%20interferes%20with%20military%20movement%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOperationally%2C%20the%20sidelining%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20ostensibly%20for%20the%20cover%20of%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%E2%80%99%20Act%20not%20being%20available%20from%20parts%20of%20the%20Valley%2C%20shows%20intent%20to%20retrench%20the%20military%20from%20its%20traditional%20remit%20as%20the%20last%20bastion%20on%20internal%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20was%20the%20need%20for%20importing%20a%20retired%20CAPF%20chief%20as%20adviser%20to%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20when%20the%20commanding%20general%20of%20Spear%20Corps%20was%20near%20at%20hand%20and%20when%20two%20divisional%20level%20formations%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20army%20and%20the%20other%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%20are%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AFSPA%20could%20have%20been%20re-promulgated%20under%20its%20Paragraph%203%2C%20by%20a%20mere%20declaration%20by%20the%20Governor%20of%20the%20Valley%20as%20a%20Disturbed%20Area.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20while%20in%20aid%20to%20civil%20authority%2C%20the%20Army%20is%20covered%20by%20the%20indemnity%20clause%20included%20in%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(or%20whatever%20the%20Hindi%20term%20the%20statute%20now%20goes%20by).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20military%20is%20a%20blunt%20instrument.%20But%20from%20recent%20killing%20of%20Muslim%20passengers%20by%20a%20railway%20cop%3B%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Muslim%20youth%20forced%20to%20chant%20the%20national%20anthem%20by%20cops%20beating%20him%3B%20and%20the%20setting%20upon%20of%20girl%20students%20of%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%20by%20baton%20wielding%20police%2C%20show%20there%20is%20no%20substitute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20ethic%20of%20political%20subservience%20of%20CAPF%20needs%20contrasting%20against%20the%20professional%20ethic%20of%20the%20Army.%20The%20Army%2C%20though%20subordinate%20to%20political%20masters%2C%20can%20only%20deviate%20from%20the%20professional%20ethic%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENormally%2C%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20reading%20of%20national%20security%20takes%20second%20place%20to%20political%20considerations%20of%20political%20decision%20makers.%20The%20military%20can%20validly%20input%20decisions%2C%20but%20not%20disobey%20them.%20The%20political%20decision%20maker%20does%20not%20owe%20the%20military%20an%20explanation%2C%20but%20is%20democratically%20answerable%20to%20the%20people%20%E2%80%93%20through%20the%20parliament%20and%20at%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20abnormal%20times%2C%20there%20are%20limits%20to%20obedience.%20And%2C%20the%20times%20%E2%80%93%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20previous%20section%20%E2%80%93%20are%20abnormal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20milieu%2C%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20mandate%20is%20independent%20of%20and%20in%20contradistinction%20to%20its%20political%20subordination.%20The%20Army%20cannot%20let%20go%20of%20its%20moorings%20on%20a%20parochial%20political%20say%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20political%20inertness%20is%20limited%20by%20its%20institutional%20self-regard.%20The%20political%20cannot%20will%20the%20military%20out%20of%20existence%20and%20the%20military%20cannot%20wilfully%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20explanatory%20variables%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20political%20facets%20have%20been%20explored%20with%20Manipur%20as%20backdrop.%20The%20first%20is%20majoritarian%20incest%2C%20between%20the%20local%20and%20the%20national.%20The%20second%20is%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20the%20military%20in%20a%20sphere%20of%20its%20professional%20mandate%20and%20competence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaken%20together%2C%20they%20forecast%20a%20national%20disaster%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clue%20is%20in%20the%20latest%20Big%20Lie%3A%20the%20risk%20of%20civilian%20casualties%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emust%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0stay%20the%20Leviathan%E2%80%99s%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20corollary%20is%20to%20let%20majoritarian%20mobs%20be.%20Rather%20than%20nipping%20their%20sway%20at%20the%20outset%20with%20a%20bullet%20below%20the%20knee%2C%20allow%20them%20maraud%20through%20a%20minority%20neighbourhood%2C%20killing%2C%20raping%2C%20burning.%20Demolitions%20can%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20allow%20majoritarian%20mobs%20play%2C%20the%20professional%20military%20requires%20neutering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20de-facto%20change%20to%20the%20Constitution%20has%20already%20been%20made%20that%20has%20it%20that%20some%20are%20more%20equal%20than%20others.%20This%20puts%20a%20lie%20to%20the%20last%20Modi%20phrase%2C%20%E2%80%98One%20House%20%E2%80%93%20One%20Law%E2%80%99%2C%20coined%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20supported%20mob-militias%20will%20administer%20the%20de-jure%20constitutional%20shift%20to%20dissenters%2C%20with%20the%20military%20defenestrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20is%20a%20test%20bed%20of%20New%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAli%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20strategic%20analyst%20and%20this%20article%20was%20originally%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faliahd66.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-big-fat-fib-on-the-utility-of%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20his%20Substack%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692183641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095357%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.01-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-is-a-test-bed-of-new-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20political%20facets%20are%20currently%20at%20play%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20first%20is%20majoritarian%20incest%2C%20between%20the%20local%20and%20the%20national.%20The%20second%20is%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20the%20military%20in%20a%20sphere%20of%20its%20professional%20mandate%20and%20competence.%20Taken%20together%2C%20they%20for