ief%20minister%2C%20and%20with%2015%20out%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2032%20MLAs%20taking%20the%20same%20position%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstubborn%E2%80%9D%20insistence%20on%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20prolonging%20if%20not%20exacerbating%20the%20problem.%20A%20new%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20no%20doubt%20will%20be%20Meitei%2C%20would%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20start%20some%20sort%20of%20peace%20process%20and%20it%20would%20also%20appease%20the%20Kuki%20community%2C%20who%20are%2016%25%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FkK4afNQe8fg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitongbam%20is%20a%20Meitei%20who%20has%20faced%20violent%20threats%20from%20Meitei%20organisations%20like%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%20because%20of%20the%20stand%20he%E2%80%99s%20taken%20on%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitongbam%20makes%20clear%20that%20the%20situation%20could%20have%20been%20nipped%20in%20the%20bud%20as%20early%20as%20May%203%20or%204%20if%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20acted.%20He%20says%20it%20was%20negligence%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Biren%20Singh%20not%20to%20do%20so.%20When%20asked%20if%20this%20negligence%20was%20followed%20or%20succeeded%20by%20a%20measure%20of%20complicity%20in%20wanting%20the%20crisis%20to%20continue%2C%20Loitongbam%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20a%20problem%20back%20home%20if%20he%20were%20to%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmongst%20the%20issues%20that%20are%20discussed%20in%20the%20interview%20is%20the%20Meitei%20demand%20to%20replace%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20the%20Kuki%20demand%20to%20restrain%20and%20stop%20Manipur%20police%20entering%20the%20hill%20areas%2C%20the%20army%20request%20for%20restraint%20on%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20who%20block%20roads%20and%20hold%20up%20army%20convoys%2C%20the%20Meitei%20perception%20of%20a%20land%20imbalance%20and%20their%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Kuki%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%2C%20which%20they%20say%20means%20a%20separate%20state%20or%20union%20territory.%20There%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20substantial%20discussion%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20crisis%20and%20what%20his%20silence%20%E2%80%93%20now%20limited%20comments%20%E2%80%93%20suggest%20of%20his%20attitude%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitongbam%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20to%20come%20together%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20government%2C%20and%20throw%20up%20out%20of%20the%20box%20ideas%20and%20start%20discussing%20them.%20He%20says%20although%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20apparent%20to%20people%20outside%20Manipur%2C%20this%20process%20has%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692176145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16142156%2FKT-16-August.00_57_01_06.Still001.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwatch-amit-shahs-lok-sabha-speech-has-made-things-worse-in-manipur-irresponsible-not-to-remove-biren%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Babloo%20Loitongbam%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20to%20come%20together%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20government%2C%20and%20throw%20up%20out%20of%20the%20box%20ideas%20and%20start%20discussing%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwatch-amit-shahs-lok-sabha-speech-has-made-things-worse-in-manipur-irresponsible-not-to-remove-biren%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyundai%20signs%20deal%20to%2