generation%20immigrants%20to%20the%20US%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F2673171%5C%22%3Espeak%20English%20fluently%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0but%20not%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnglish%20is%20economically%20and%20culturally%20beneficial%20to%20them%2C%20but%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20languages%20are%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F14688624%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F14688624%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F14688624%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20look%20at%20where%20the%20most%20Indigenous%20languages%20are%20endangered%20reveals%20the%20impact%20of%20previous%20migrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%2098%20percent%20of%20Indigenous%20languages%20in%20the%20US%20and%2089%20percent%20of%20Indigenous%20languages%20in%20Australia%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnologue.com%2Finsights%2Fhow-many-languages-endangered%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20endangered%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%20have%20a%20colonial%20history%20and%20have%20seen%20mass%20immigration%20from%20Europe%20in%20previous%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20earlier%20migrations%20affect%20Indigenous%20languages%20to%20this%20day%20%E2%80%93%20we%20continue%20losing%20languages%20in%20these%20countries%20because%20speakers%20no%20longer%20pass%20them%20on%20to%20future%20generations%20and%20switch%20to%20English%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20today%E2%80%99s%20migration%20will%20likely%20be%20tomorrow%E2%80%99s%20language%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForced%20migration%20plays%20a%20large%20role%20in%20current%20migration%20patterns.%20According%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unhcr.org%2Fglobal-trends-report-2022%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Trends%20Report%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20than%20108%20million%20people%20were%20forcibly%20displaced%20in%202022.%20About%2061%20million%20of%20them%20were%20displaced%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.internal-displacement.org%2Fglobal-report%2Fgrid2023%2F%5C%22%3Ewithin%20their%20own%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20those%20internally%20displaced%20had%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20because%20of%20environmental%20disasters%2C%20such%20as%20floods%20and%20storms.%20The%20remaining%20people%20were%20internally%20displaced%20by%20conflict%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20internal%20displacement%20in%20Europe%20and%20Central%20Asia%20in%202022%20was%20due%20to%20conflict%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20almost%20all%20internal%20displacement%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20East%20Asia%20and%20the%20Pacific%20was%20caused%20by%20weather-related%20disasters%2C%20such%20as%20floods%20and%20storms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20linguistically%20diverse%20countries%20are%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20East%20Asia%20and%20the%20Pacific%2C%20those%20regions%20particularly%20affected%20by%20environmental%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPapua%20New%20Guinea%20has%20at%20least%20nine%20million%20inhabitants.%20Between%20them%20they%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnologue.com%2Fcountry%2FPG%2F%5C%22%3Espeak%20839%20different%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20313%20of%20those%20languages%20endangered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20300%2C000%20inhabitants%20of%20Vanuatu%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnologue.com%2Fcountry%2FVU%2F%5C%22%3Espeak%20108%20different%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20of%20which%20more%20than%20half%20are%20endangered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnologue.com%2Fcountry%2FID%2F%5C%22%3EIndonesia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20another%20704%20living%20languages%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnologue.com%2Fcountry%2FIN%2F%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20424%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnologue.com%2Fcountry%2FPH%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20Philippines%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20175.%20Almost%20half%20of%20the%20languages%20spoken%20in%20these%20three%20countries%20are%20endangered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20one%20third%20of%20the%20languages%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funesdoc.unesco.org%2Fark%3A%2F48223%2Fpf0000192416%5C%22%3Econsidered%20endangered%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20spoken%20in%20those%20five%20countries%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20numbers%20of%20already%20endangered%20languages%20combined%20with%20the%20large%20numbers%20of%20people%20displaced%20by%20environmental%20disasters%20make%20South%20Asia%2C%20East%20Asia%20and%20the%20Pacific%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20future%20language%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20endangered%20languages%20are%20spoken%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funesdoc.unesco.org%2Fark%3A%2F48223%2Fpf0000187026%5C%22%3Ea%20small%20geographic%20area%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20have%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fnews%2Fdatablog%2F2011%2Fapr%2F15%2Flanguage-extinct-endangered%5C%22%3Eonly%20a%20few%20hundred%20speakers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20speakers%20of%20those%20languages%20leave%20their%20small%20communities%20and%20scatter%20%E2%80%93%20for%20whatever%20reasons%20%E2%80%93%20it%20becomes%20less%20likely%20that%20they%20will%20pass%20on%20these%20languages%20to%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20their%20small%20communities%2C%20these%20languages%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20little%20economic%20and%20cultural%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20forced%20migration%20is%20that%20people%20lose%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20lots%20of%20the%20things%20that%20people%20propose%20to%20preserve%20languages%20%E2%80%93%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcompass.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1111%2Fj.1749-818X.2007.00004.x%5C%22%3Eensuring%20communities%20remain%20together%2C%20have%20a%20viable%20environment%20to%20live%20in%20and%20ways%20of%20making%20a%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20necessarily%20apply%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20reasons%20for%20language%20loss%2C%20and%20migration%20is%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20puzzle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20those%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20where%20we%20find%20many%20of%20the%20endangered%20languages%2C%20environmental%20disasters%20are%20a%20major%20driving%20force%20of%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20forced%20migration%20%E2%80%93%20and%20subsequent%20threat%20to%20languages%20%E2%80%93%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20accelerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanouschkafoltz%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EAnouschka%20Foltz%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20associate%20professor%20in%20English%20linguistics%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20English%20Studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Graz%20in%20Austria.%20Before%20coming%20to%20Graz%20she%20was%20a%20lecturer%20in%20psycholinguistics%20at%20Bangor%20University%20in%20Wales.%20Her%20research%20is%20in%20the%20area%20of%20psycholinguistics%2C%20and%20her%20work%20focuses%20on%20adult%20language%20processing%2C%20L1%20and%20L2%20language%20acquisition%20as%20well%20as%20multilingualism.%20She%20is%20also%20interested%20in%20language%20rights%20and%20access%20to%20language.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOriginally%20published%20under%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0by%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E360info%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%84%A2.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692172158000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191750%2FIMG_0112-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fclimate-change-is-killing-languages%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Forced%20migration%20is%20a%20major%20cause%20of%20language%20extinction.%20Environmental%20disasters%20are%20driving%20these%20displacements%20in%20the%20very%20regions%20richest%20in%20languages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fclimate-change-is-killing-languages%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20of%20Haryana%20family%20dead%20in%20landslide%20near%20Rishikesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692171452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102765829%2Cimgsize-72398.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fbodies-of-haryana-couple-recovered-from-landslide-site-in-uttarakhands-pauri-garhwal-2-children-still-missing%2Farticleshow%2F102765303.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bodies%20of%20a%20couple%20from%20Haryana's%20Kurukshetra%20were%20recovered%20on%20Wednesday%20from%20Night%20Paradise%20Camp%2C%20a%20tourist%20camp%20site%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Pauri%20Garhwal%20district%2C%20which%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20landslide%20on%20August%2014%20following%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20taking%20the%20death%20toll%20to%20three.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22GAURAV%20TALWAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fbodies-of-haryana-couple-recovered-from-landslide-site-in-uttarakhands-pauri-garhwal-2-children-still-missing%2Farticleshow%2F102765303.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Why%20Wasn't%20Justice%20Muralidhar%20Brought%20to%20Supreme%20Court%3F'%3A%20Three%20Noted%20Legal%20Minds%20Ask%20SC%20Collegium%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F28192720%2FScreen-Shot-2020-02-28-at-7.27.03-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20retired%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20two%20other%20legal%20luminaries%20have%20together%20written%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fa-question-for-supreme-court-8894242%2F%5C%22%3E%20opinion%20piece%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20asking%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20collegium%20why%20it%20%E2%80%9Crefused%20to%20bring%20Justice%20S.%20Muralidhar%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20apex%20court%20despite%20his%20exemplary%20record%20as%20a%20judge%20and%20legal%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20essay%2C%20headlined%20%E2%80%98A%20question%20for%20the%20collegium%E2%80%99%2C%20appeared%20in%20the%20paper%20today%2C%20August%2016.%20It%20is%20written%20by%20Justice%20Madan%20B.%20Lokur%2C%20who%20retired%20as%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20and%20had%20once%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SC%20collegium%20which%20selects%20judges%20for%20appointment%20to%20high%20courts%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20noted%20jurist%20and%20senior%20advocate%20Fali%20Nariman%20and%20senior%20advocate%20and%20mediation%20specialist%20Sriram%20Panchu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Muralidhar%20retired%20as%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Orissa%20high%20court%20on%20August%207%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20this%20piece%20is%20to%20ask%20the%20collegium%20why%20his%20retirement%20date%20was%20not%20August%207%2C%202026%2C%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20essay%20opens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20cite%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20years%20as%20a%20lawyer%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20including%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20when%20T.N.%20Seshan%20headed%20it.%20The%20authors%20observed%20that%20his%20engagement%20with%20the%20law%20has%20been%20wide%20and%20deep.%20They%20note%20that%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3ELaw%2C%20Poverty%20and%20Legal%20Aid%3A%20Access%20to%20Criminal%20Justice%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20seminal%20contribution%20to%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20an%20impressive%20bio%20acquired%20%E2%80%9Clegendary%20proportions%2C%E2%80%9D%20write%20the%20authors%2C%20once%20the%20judge%20came%20to%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court.%20He%20served%20there%20between%202006%20and%202020.%20The%20authors%20note%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20many%20significant%20cases%20and%20the%20balance%20he%20struck%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-muralidhar-farewell-speech-full%5C%22%3EJustice%20Muralidhar%20on%20the%20Distinction%20Between%20Neutrality%20and%20Impartiality%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20key%20judgements%20that%20Justice%20Muralidhar%20authored%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3ENaz%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFoundation%3C%2Fem%3E%20one%20that%20decriminalised%20consensual%20homosexuality%2C%20the%20conviction%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Sajjan%20Kumar%20for%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots%2C%20the%20sentencing%20of%2016%20policemen%20for%20the%20killings%20of%2038%20Muslims%20in%20Hashimpura%20and%20the%20bail%20to%20Gautam%20Navlakha%2C%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20note%20especially%20how%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20him%20ensured%20ambulance%20services%20to%20riot-affected%20areas%20in%20northeast%20Delhi%20in%202020%2C%20through%20a%20late%20night%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20appointment%20as%20Orissa%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20the%20writers%20say%2C%20changed%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20hitherto%20quiet%20court%20which%20henceforth%20saw%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20have%20a%20glance%20at%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Orissa%20High%20Court.%20Its%20filings%2C%20records%2C%20fees%20are%20in%20e-mode%2C%20it%20has%20paperless%20benches%2C%20hybrid%20hearings%20and%20e-libraries%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20write.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20his%20efforts%20to%20design%20a%20better%20system%20came%20with%20significant%20judicial%20work%20pressure.%20The%20authors%20write%20that%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20bench%20disposed%20of%2033%2C322%20cases%20in%20his%2031%20months%20and%20delivered%20545%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guard%20of%20honour%20he%20received%20at%20his%20retirement%20was%20enormous%20and%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20happened%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20noted%2C%20observing%20that%20the%20judge%20at%2062%20had%20much%20more%20to%20give%20that%20the%20judiciary%20has%20lost%20a%20treasured%20asset%20with%20his%20retirement.%20Hard%20questions%20must%20thus%20be%20asked%20of%20the%20collegium%2C%20they%20write.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FlVxqEaOZGhI%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22This%20Judge%20Was%20So%20Outstanding%20Modi%20Ensured%20He%20Never%20Made%20It%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20such%20merit%20on%20display%2C%20along%20with%20matchless%20integrity%20and%20probity%2C%20on%20what%20grounds%20was%20he%20denied%20his%20rightful%20place%3F%20Sometimes%20these%20questions%20are%20asked%20rhetorically%2C%20but%20his%20case%20is%20a%20cause%20celebre%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20case%20that%20comes%20up%20to%20illustrate%20the%20workings%20of%20a%20system%2C%20which%20must%20be%20seized%20upon%20if%20we%20want%20to%20examine%20and%20improve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20writers%20also%20asked%20why%20Justice%20Muralidhar%20was%20not%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20made%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20larger%20and%20chartered%20High%20Court%20of%20Madras%2C%20a%20move%20initiated%20by%20the%20collegium%2C%20not%20acted%20upon%20by%20government%20and%20not%20pursued%20by%20the%20collegium%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collegium%E2%80%99s%20resolution%20in%20April%20recalling%20its%20recommendation%20for%20this%20transfer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgovernment-sc-collegium-justice-muralidhar%5C%22%3Ewrote%20V.%20Venkatesan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20made%20its%20helplessness%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20defiance%20for%20over%20six%20months%20quite%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answers%2C%20they%20write%2C%20are%20not%20blowing%20in%20the%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692170456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F28192720%2FScreen-Shot-2020-02-28-at-7.27.03-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-muralidhar-supreme-court-collegium-oped%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'With%20such%20merit%20on%20display%2C%20along%20with%20matchless%20integrity%20and%20probity%2C%20on%20what%20grounds%20was%20he%20denied%20his%20rightful%20place%3F'%20Justice%20Madan%20B.%20Lokur%2C%20along%20with%20Fali%20Nariman%20and%20Sriram%20Panchu%2C%20asked%20the%20Collegium.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-muralidhar-supreme-court-collegium-oped%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Coach%20Who%20Accused%20Haryana%20Minister%20Sandeep%20Singh%20of%20Sexual%20Harassment%20Suspended%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16120402%2FF3kZY82bcAAjb0U.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Haryana%20sports%20department%20has%20suspended%20the%20woman%20junior%20athletic%20coach%20who%20had%20accused%20state%20minister%20Sandeep%20Singh%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-sports-department-suspends-woman-coach-accusing-minister-of-sexual-misconduct-101692122213332.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20order%2C%20issued%20on%20August%2011%20by%20sports%20department%20director%20Yashendra%20Singh%2C%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20services%20of%20the%20Junior%20Athletic%20Coach%2C%20(posted%20in%20the%20office%20of)%20district%20sports%20officer%2C%20Panchkula%20are%20placed%20under%20suspension%20with%20immediate%20effect%20without%20prejudice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20not%20list%20any%20reason%20for%20her%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coach%20had%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20Singh%20in%20December%202022%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20charges%20of%20stalking%2C%20illegal%20confinement%2C%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh%2Fwoman-coach-sexual-harassment-allegations-haryana-minister-sandeep-singh-8894580%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20have%20been%20suspended.%20Pressure%20is%20being%20mounted%20on%20me%20to%20hammer%20out%20a%20compromise%20(to%20withdraw%20the%20case).%20I%20have%20not%20been%20intimated%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20my%20suspension.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20they%20have%20taken%20this%20step.%20This%20is%20yet%20another%20way%20for%20the%20government%20to%20pressurise%20me%2C%20but%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20coach%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20handed%20the%20suspension%20order%20at%20her%20residence%20on%20Monday%20evening%20despite%20attending%20office%20that%20day%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20order%2C%20she%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20subsistence%20allowance%20as%20admissible%20under%20Rule%2083%20of%20Haryana%20Civil%20Services%20(general)%20Rules%2C%202016%20and%20her%20post%20during%20the%20suspension%20period%20will%20remain%20the%20office%20of%20district%20sports%20officer%2C%20Panchkula%20where%20she%20is%20posted%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20relieved%20of%20the%20sports%20and%20youth%20affairs%20portfolio%20a%20week%20after%20being%20booked%2C%20however%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20hold%20charge%20of%20the%20printing%20and%20stationery%20department%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20a%20former%20Olympian%20and%20captain%20of%20the%20national%20hockey%20team%2C%20has%20dismissed%20the%20accusations%20as%20false.%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20also%20came%20out%20in%20his%20support%20and%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Can%20allegation%20does%20not%20make%20a%20person%20guilty%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692168560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16120402%2FF3kZY82bcAAjb0U.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwoman-coach-who-accused-haryana-minister-sandeep-singh-of-sexual-harassment-suspended%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20suspension%20order%20does%20not%20list%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20woman%20coach's%20suspension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwoman-coach-who-accused-haryana-minister-sandeep-singh-of-sexual-harassment-suspended%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Gains%20and%20Who%20Loses%3F%20A%20Report%20From%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Red%20Fort%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20is%20improving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20everyday%20reality%20for%20those%20living%20in%20the%20civil%20war%20situation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20since%20May%203%2C%20however%2C%20is%20proof%20that%20the%20danger%20to%20their%20life%20and%20property%20is%20nowhere%20near%20%E2%80%98improved%E2%80%99.%20The%20lines%20between%20the%20communities%20are%20only%20getting%20firmer%20with%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20reality%20emanating%20from%20the%20disturbing%20situation%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20three%20northeastern%20women%20well-known%20for%20their%20contribution%20to%20their%20respective%20societies%20and%20the%20region%20in%20general%20%E2%80%93%20Angela%20Rangad%20from%20Meghalaya%2C%20Jarjum%20Ete%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Roshmi%20Goswami%20from%20Assam%20%E2%80%93%20embarked%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Manipur%20on%20August%203.%20They%20were%20accompanied%20by%20Delhi-based%20activist%20Syeda%20Hameed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20women%20state%20in%20a%20report%20that%20has%20sprung%20out%20of%20their%20visit%20to%20Manipur%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20women%20from%20different%20places%20and%20different%20affiliations%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20their%20difference%20is%20also%20in%20their%20respective%20faiths.%20One%20is%20a%20Muslim%2C%20another%20a%20Hindu%2C%20one%20a%20Christian%20and%20another%20from%20an%20indigenous%20tribal%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20their%20visit%20was%20primarily%20intended%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98goodwill%E2%80%99%20gesture%20from%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20the%20team%20ended%20up%20putting%20together%20a%20report%20to%20document%20what%20they%20saw%2C%20heard%20and%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20multiple%20voices%20from%20both%20the%20warring%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis%20%E2%80%93%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore.%20The%20report%20includes%20recommendations%20collated%20from%20the%20people%20they%20met%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide%20to%20better%20their%20condition.%20It%20also%20documents%20certain%20red%20flags%20coming%20in%20the%20way%20of%20peace%2C%20including%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20keep%20faith%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20even%20while%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20demand%20his%20removal%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20failing%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20report%20by%20the%20four%20women%20is%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Gains%3F%20Who%20Loses%3F%3A%20Interim%20Reflections%20from%20Manipur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBy%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EDr.%20Syeda%20Hameed%3A%20Mentor%20%E2%80%93%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyan%2C%20Founder%20member%20South%20Asians%20For%20Human%20Rights.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EDr.%20Roshmi%20Goswami%3A%20National%20Council%20Member%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyan%2C%20Co-Chair%20South%20Asians%20For%20Human%20Rights%2C%20Co-founder%2C%20North%20East%20Network.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EJarjum%20G%20Ete%3A%20President%20Emeritus%2C%20All%20India%20Union%20of%20Forest%20Working%20People%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EAngela%20Rangad%3A%20TUR%20%E2%80%93%20Thma%20U%20Rangli%20Juki%2C%20KAM%20Meghalaya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWAS%20IT%20THE%20RIGHT%20TIME%20TO%20VISIT%20MANIPUR%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20a%20team%20of%20four%20women%20from%20different%20places%20and%20having%20different%20affiliations.%20Three%20of%20us%20from%20the%20North%20East%20and%20one%20from%20Delhi%2C%20having%20different%20ethnicities%20and%20four%20different%20religions%20%E2%80%93%20Christian%2C%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%20and%20Indigenous%20tribal%20faith.%20For%20one%20of%20us%20the%20process%20of%20connecting%20with%20Manipur%20during%20this%20moment%20of%20unprecedented%20crisis%20had%20already%20begun%20by%20way%20of%20a%20three%20day%20closed%20door%20meeting%20in%20a%20very%20private%20enabling%20feminist%20space%20where%20women%20from%20five%20different%20communities%20of%20Manipur%20were%20able%20to%20come%20together%20to%20talk.%20This%20visit%20came%20about%20from%20that%20closed%20door%20meeting%20and%20was%20initially%20planned%20as%20a%20Goodwill%20visit.%20But%20as%20we%20traveled%20through%20battle%20ravaged%20Manipur%20the%20objective%20of%20our%20visit%20kept%20evolving%2C%20incorporating%20new%20perspectives%20and%20taking%20different%20directions.%20Eventually%20it%20was%20just%20a%20%E2%80%98mission%20of%20listening%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20first%20in%20a%20series%20of%20proposed%20visits%20that%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20undertake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM-300x182.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM-1024x621.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668279%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20landed%20in%20Imphal%20on%20the%203rd%20of%20August.%20A%20most%20contentious%20day%20to%20arrive%20as%20it%20marked%20three%20months%20since%20the%20fateful%20day%20of%20May%203rd%2C%20and%20the%20Kuki%20community%20had%20proposed%20to%20hold%20a%20mass%20burial%20programme%20of%20their%20dead%20on%20that%20day.%20The%20proposal%20was%20to%20bury%2035%20dead%20including%203%20women%20lying%20in%20the%20Churachandpur%20district%20hospital%20morgue%20at%20S.%20Boljang%20village.%20The%20proposed%20burial%20was%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20a%20hugely%20controversial%20and%20charged%20event%20as%20the%20proposed%20burial%20grounds%20were%20being%20claimed%20by%20both%20sides%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20Kukis%20primarily%20led%20by%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20ITLF%20and%20by%20the%20Coordination%20Committee%20For%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%20for%20the%20Meiteis.%20Mass%20condolence%20ceremonies%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20deceased%20were%20conducted%20at%20the%20peace%20ground%20at%20Turbong%20and%20in%20other%20Kuki%20areas%20and%20were%20already%20over%20by%20the%20time%20we%20reached%20our%20destination%2C%20and%20the%20burial%20was%20however%20deferred%20for%20another%20week%20by%20the%20Manipur%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20asked%20both%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities%20to%20maintain%20status%20quo%20and%20to%20arrive%20at%20an%20amicable%20settlement%20during%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20this%20flashpoint%20of%20fresh%20confrontation%2C%20the%20entire%20period%20of%20our%20visit%20was%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%98flare%20up%E2%80%99%20period%20which%20was%20highly%20charged%2C%20each%20day%20bringing%20new%20challenges%20of%20heightened%20aggressive%20and%20combat%20posturing%20by%20all%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20groups%2C%20Meira%20Paibis%2C%20Armed%20volunteers%2C%20State%20and%20Central%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20Military.%20We%20were%20therefore%20literally%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20%E2%80%98events%20and%20incidents%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20a%20lived%20experience%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Manipur%20battleground%E2%80%99.%20This%20also%20determined%20where%20we%20could%20go%20and%20where%20we%20could%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20arrival%20at%20Imphal%2C%20we%20met%20a%20cross%20section%20of%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20people%20%E2%80%93%20old%20friends%20who%20we%20had%20journeyed%20together%20with%20in%20earlier%20struggles%20and%20movements%20as%20well%20as%20new%20acquaintances.%20The%20conversations%20that%20evening%20were%20very%20open%20and%20trusting%20and%20provided%20some%20context%20as%20well%20as%20questions.%20We%20were%20to%20visit%20Churachandpur%20or%20as%20some%20like%20to%20call%20it%20today%20Lamka%2C%20the%20very%20next%20day%20after%20our%20arrival.%20But%20after%20the%20tensions%20of%203rd%20August%2C%20we%20were%20advised%20to%20visit%20Tengnoupal%20%E2%80%93%20another%20Kuki%20stronghold%20District%20instead.%20An%20important%20District%20that%20has%20the%20Asian%20highway%20connecting%20Moreh%2C%20here%20we%20witnessed%20the%20massive%20community%20mobilisation%20particularly%20of%20women%20not%20only%20to%20support%20and%20run%20Relief%20camps%20but%20also%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20resistance%20%2F%20defense%20efforts.%20Next%20day%2C%20the%204th%20of%20August%20we%20decided%20to%20leave%20Imphal%20at%20the%20crack%20of%20dawn%20to%20head%20for%20Churachandpur%2C%20only%20for%20us%20to%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20events%20of%20yet%20another%20volatile%20day%20this%20conflict%20had%20seen.%20After%20having%20managed%20to%20negotiate%20our%20way%20through%20several%20Meira%20Paibi%20barricades%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20reach%20the%20border%20village%20of%20Kwakta%2C%20when%20our%20Pangal%20(Meitei%20Muslim)%20driver%20flatly%20refused%20to%20go%20any%20further%20after%20we%20had%20cleared%20every%20other%20hurdle.%20The%20incessant%20shelling%20and%20sniping%20from%20the%20surrounding%20hills%20unnerved%20him.%20It%20was%20the%20morning%20when%20three%20people%20had%20just%20been%20killed%20at%203%20am%20while%20still%20sleeping%2C%20and%20the%20bodies%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20retrieved.%20Meira%20Paibis%20from%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20Bishnupur%20district%20and%20armed%20volunteers%20were%20pouring%20in%20to%20join%20the%20mourning%20family%20members%20and%20were%20also%20readying%20themselves%20to%20protest%2Fretaliate.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20charged%20situation%2C%20and%20yet%20we%20might%20have%20taken%20a%20chance%20and%20walked%20through%20no%20man%E2%80%99s%20land%20across%20what%20everyone%20there%20describes%20as%20the%20LOC%2C%20where%20our%20Kuki%20friends%20were%20waiting%20to%20receive%20us%2C%20but%20there%20were%20people%20with%20limitations%20in%20our%20team%20and%20we%20had%20to%20be%20mindful.%20Our%20return%20journey%20across%20Imphal%20towards%20our%20hotel%20was%20also%20fraught%20with%20tension%20as%20the%20anger%20and%20anguish%20about%20the%20deaths%20that%20day%20was%20palpable%20when%20we%20were%20stopped%20at%20every%20crossing%20by%20groups%20of%20people%2C%20mainly%20women%20who%20demanded%20to%20see%20our%20IDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20journey%20to%20Kangpokpi%20the%20next%20day%20was%20relatively%20easier%20and%20smoother%2C%20but%20what%20we%20heard%20and%20saw%20there%20left%20us%20heartbroken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20short%20visit%20we%20interacted%20and%20had%20wide%20ranging%20discussions%20with%20a%20cross%20section%20of%20people%20(Meitei%2C%20Kuki%20Zo%20as%20well%20as%20Naga).%20We%20met%20organizations%2C%20women%20and%20student%20leaders%2C%20concerned%20individuals%2C%20experts%20from%20human%20rights%20and%20environmental%20movements%2C%20peace%20activists%20and%20negotiators%2C%20journalists%2C%20researchers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20writers%20and%20theater%20personalities%2C%20students%2C%20relief%20providers%2C%20church%20workers%20and%20others.%20We%20also%20met%20survivors%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20assault%20and%20killings%2C%20families%20of%20disappeared%20peoples%2C%20displaced%20people%20and%20individual%20voices%20against%20the%20drug%20cartel.%20There%20were%20several%20narratives%20%E2%80%93%20some%20more%20dominant%20than%20others%20and%20also%20constantly%20changing%20as%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EANGUISHED%20NARRATIVES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20striking%20expression%20cutting%20across%20both%20the%20Kukis%20and%20Meitei%20people%20we%20interacted%20with%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20situation%2C%20was%20their%20unequivocal%20assertion%20that%20the%20present%20regime%20both%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20the%20state%20are%20clearly%20and%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20continued%20violence%20and%20complete%20anarchy%20in%20the%20state.%20People%20were%20unanimous%20in%20saying%20that%20if%20the%20violence%20was%20controlled%20and%20reined%20in%20in%20the%20first%20few%20days%20of%20its%20outburst%20in%20May%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20accelerated%20the%20way%20it%20did%20and%20they%20would%20not%20be%20in%20the%20present%20state%20that%20they%20are%20in.%20They%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20many%20of%20the%20sexual%20violations%20and%20killings%20that%20happened%20after%20the%203rd%20and%204th%20of%20May%20could%20perhaps%20have%20been%20avoided.%20The%20issue%20of%20command%20responsibility%20and%20state%20accountability%20rang%20loud%20and%20clear%20from%20every%20quarter%20and%20category%20of%20people.%20In%20Kwakta%20when%20we%20knelt%20down%20to%20pay%20our%20condolences%20to%20the%20grief%20stricken%20widow%20of%20Prem%20Kumar%20Yumnam%20who%20was%20brutally%20killed%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20earlier%2C%20she%20screamed%20out%20-%E2%80%98%20If%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20controlled%20this%20violence%20three%20months%20ago%20my%20husband%20would%20be%20alive%20today.%20Why%20is%20he%20still%20silent%3F%E2%80%99%20Both%20sides%20believe%20that%20the%20violence%20and%20aggression%20has%20been%20deliberately%20left%20to%20fester%20and%20as%20new%20elements%20are%20added%20the%20situation%20gets%20aggravated%20every%20single%20day.%20The%20Manipur%20crisis%20is%20therefore%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20both%20the%20culpability%20and%20incapability%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20led%20by%20Narendra%20Modi.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20petulant%20and%20arrogant%20silence%20and%20lack%20of%20empathy%20for%20the%20affected%20people%20shows%20a%20complete%20disregard%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20and%20is%20deeply%20insulting%20to%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM.jpg%201198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM-1022x1024.jpg%201022w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20institutions%20have%20collapsed%20and%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20sense%20of%20state%20inaction%20with%20bodies%20lying%20in%20the%20morgues%20and%20the%20state%20not%20enabling%20a%20process%20of%20identification%20and%20closure%20for%20grieving%20families.%20Instead%2C%20the%20BJP%20regime%20(%20Cf%3A%20Tushar%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20claims)%20is%20seen%20indulging%20in%20its%20typical%20diversionary%20blame%20game%20by%20labeling%20the%20unclaimed%20bodies%20as%20those%20belonging%20to%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20while%20families%20wait%20in%20anguish%20and%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20were%20also%20raised%20about%20undertrials%20in%20the%20jails%20in%20Imphal%20and%20other%20Meitei%20dominated%20districts%2C%20with%20Kukis%20having%20no%20access%20to%20their%20loved%20ones%20and%20of%20not%20even%20knowing%20if%20they%20are%20still%20alive.%20As%20one%20person%20pointed%20out%2C%20the%20state%20has%20been%20%E2%80%98strategically%20absent%E2%80%99.%20This%20strategic%20absence%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20the%20DNA%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20when%20they%20are%20unable%20or%20unwilling%20to%20take%20action%20either%20because%20of%20incapability%20or%20calculations%20around%20some%20electoral%20gains%20or%20losses.%20People%20simply%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20absence%20and%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20culpability%20was%20particularly%20glaring%20in%20the%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20the%20Kuki%20Zo%20community.%20While%20we%20had%20read%20about%20the%20extent%20and%20depth%20of%20the%20violations%20that%20had%20taken%20place%20since%20May%203%2C%20the%20first%20hand%20accounts%20of%20brutality%20and%20mayhem%20was%20extremely%20shocking%2C%20especially%20accounts%20of%20the%20sexual%20violence%20and%20the%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20any%20norms%20of%20humanity.%20Serious%20doubts%20were%20also%20raised%20about%20the%20partisan%20and%20communal%20role%20played%20by%20higher%20ups%20in%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20narrative%20is%20that%20the%20core%20issue%20is%20not%20even%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20separate%20Kuki%20administration%20or%20clash%20with%20militants%20in%20different%20locations%20but%20that%20it%20is%20essentially%20a%20geo-political%20conflict%20driven%20by%20people%20with%20a%20deep%20rooted%20political%20agenda.%20The%20%E2%80%98strategic%20absence%E2%80%99%20and%20silence%20of%20the%20Centre%20seems%20to%20lend%20credibility%20to%20this%20narrative.%20Along%20the%20same%20narrative%20a%20question%20that%20was%20raised%20by%20several%20people%20including%20those%20who%20have%20been%20directly%20affected%20is%20%E2%80%9CWho%20gains%3F%E2%80%9D%20from%20allowing%20this%20impasse%20to%20continue%20and%20for%20the%20violence%20to%20fester.%20Is%20this%20lingering%20conflict%20a%20cover%20up%20or%20a%20diversion%20from%20other%20things%20that%20are%20going%20on%3F%20Linkages%20to%20the%20poppy%20cultivation%20and%20the%20drug%20cartel%20and%20drug%20money%20being%20used%20for%20electioneering%20was%20made%20by%20several%20people%20%E2%80%93%20some%20alluded%20to%20it%20while%20others%20were%20very%20vocal%20with%20ex%20police%20officer%20Thounaojam%20Brinda%20going%20public%20with%20evidence%20in%20asking%20%E2%80%98Is%20CM%20Biren%20Fighting%20a%20War%20against%20Drugs%20or%20For%20Drugs%3F%E2%80%99%20She%20spoke%20to%20us%20at%20length%20on%20the%20various%20aspects%20and%20operational%20strategies%20of%20the%20drug%20mafia%20and%20the%20inextricable%20nexus%20with%20the%20seats%20of%20power%20and%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20higher%20ups%20of%20all%20the%20communities.%20And%20as%20the%20impasse%20continues%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20realization%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide%20that%20ultimately%20all%20communities%20are%20expendable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20in%20conflict%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20severely%20snapped%20at%20least%20for%20now.%20Colleagues%20and%20friends%20who%20had%20lived%20together%20and%20worked%20together%20still%20maintain%20contact%20but%20the%20strains%20of%20everyday%20strife%20are%20pressing%20down%20and%20here%20and%20there%20fissures%20and%20doubt%20were%20visible.%20Amongst%20the%20women%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20this%20breakdown%20of%20ties%20is%20deeply%20felt.There%20is%20immense%20sadness%2C%20grief%20and%20regret%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20the%20incidences%20of%20barbaric%20violence.%20There%20is%20also%20huge%20rage%20and%20anger.%20It%20is%20very%20early%20yet%20and%20too%20fraught%20to%20talk%20about%20peace.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20need%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20practical%20requirements%20that%20have%20arisen%20and%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20build%20trust%20through%20a%20sense%20of%20urgent%20concerns%20common%20to%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide.%20But%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20is%20for%20a%20cessation%20of%20violence%20and%20hostilities.%20Most%20felt%20that%20this%20was%20possible%20only%20with%20the%20removal%20of%20CM%20Biren%20Singh.%20The%20call%20for%20his%20removal%20came%20from%20both%20the%20communities%20and%20debunked%20the%20narrative%20that%20he%20has%20unanimous%20support%20from%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kukis%20across%20the%20board%20reiterated%20their%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%20as%20trust%20has%20been%20broken%20and%20they%20no%20longer%20feel%20safe%20to%20be%20under%20the%20same%20jurisdiction%20as%20the%20Meiteis.%20No%20doubt%20the%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%20precedes%20the%20May%203rd%20outbreak%20of%20violence%20but%20since%20then%20and%20whatever%20has%20happened%20during%20this%20three%20month%20period%20strengthens%20the%20demand%20and%20the%20resolve%20of%20the%20Kukis%20to%20be%20separate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20582px)%2085vw%2C%20582px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22582%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM-1024x1021.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668281%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22581%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20visit%20to%20the%20relief%20camps%20and%20our%20conversations%20with%20family%20members%20and%20women%20support%20groups%20of%20the%20disappeared%20and%20a%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20violence%20has%20provided%20practical%20and%20some%20telling%20gendered%20insights%20which%20is%20being%20included%20in%20the%20section%20on%20Relief%20and%20Rehabilitation.%20The%20meeting%20with%20a%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20getting%20to%20know%20her%20story%20and%20its%20aftermath%20from%20her%20detailed%20FIR%20and%20from%20people%20around%20her%20was%20especially%20painful%20and%20shook%20us%20profoundly.%20Her%20mother%20(a%20person%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20cleaner%20in%20Imphal)%20was%20emphatic%20about%20justice%2C%20seeking%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20the%20perpetrators%20but%20not%20capital%20punishment.%20The%20silence%20and%20the%20blank%20expression%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20survivor%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mere%20child%20barely%2018%20years%20of%20age%2C%20spoke%20volumes.%20We%20tried%20to%20draw%20her%20out%20and%20finally%20got%20the%20hint%20of%20an%20impish%20smile%20when%20we%20urged%20her%20to%20think%20about%20herself%20and%20to%20tell%20us%20what%20she%20wants%20rather%20than%20what%20others%20want%20for%20her!%20She%20was%20able%20to%20articulate%20what%20she%20wanted%20and%20that%20was%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20and%20power%20of%20women%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide%20is%20simply%20astounding%20and%20also%20very%20complicated.%20As%20one%20of%20our%20team%20members%20put%20it%2C%20she%20has%20never%20seen%20this%20kind%20of%20spirit%20and%20resistance%20across%20the%20country.%20We%20met%20Kuki%20women%20sitting%20in%20the%20pelting%20rain%20and%20thick%20fog%20at%20Tengnoupal%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%20blocking%20the%20movement%20of%20RAF%20Commando%20trucks%20on%20the%20Trans%20Asian%20highway%20to%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh.%20We%20saw%20too%20the%20sensitivity%20and%20gentleness%20of%20a%20group%20of%20young%20women%20who%20have%20encircled%20a%20young%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20her%20family%20moving%20them%20out%20from%20a%20very%20public%20relief%20camp%20and%20helping%20to%20set%20up%20a%20home%20in%20a%20beautiful%20and%20secure%20homestead%20enabling%20healing%20and%20freeing%20them%20from%20constant%20media%20and%20public%20focus%20and%20supporting%20the%20whole%20family%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM.jpg%201198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM-1022x1024.jpg%201022w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668282%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20encountered%20the%20absolutely%20formidable%20force%20and%20power%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20as%20they%20enforced%20a%20Public%20curfew%20in%20Meitei%20districts%2C%20blocked%20access%20to%20Kuki%20dominated%20areas%20or%20organised%2Fparticipated%20in%20collective%20mourning%20for%20a%20slain%20youth%20from%20the%20security%20forces.%20We%20saw%20their%20power%20but%20have%20come%20back%20with%20troubling%20as%20well%20as%20complex%20questions%20about%20their%20%E2%80%98agency%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20strong%20patriarchal%20society%20like%20theirs.%20What%20was%20quite%20evident%20though%20was%20that%20unlike%20women%20from%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Naga%20communities%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20and%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20general%20do%20not%20appear%20to%20come%20under%20any%20Unified%20Command%20Structure%20and%20therefore%20defy%20any%20attempts%20at%20disciplining.%20In%20our%20team%20itself%20there%20were%20disagreements%20about%20this%20structure%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20but%20it%20was%20obvious%20that%20while%20a%20loose%20and%20amorphous%20structure%20allows%20for%20autonomy%20and%20resilience%20at%20the%20local%20level%20as%20each%20Leikai%20or%20locality%20has%20its%20own%20group%20of%20Meira%20Paibis%20with%20different%20operating%20styles%20and%20norms%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20hugely%20chaotic%20and%20unrestrainable.%20A%20keen%20sense%20of%20justice%20and%20defiance%20against%20subjugation%20or%20oppression%20is%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20the%20political%20consciousness%20of%20Meitei%20women%20in%20general%20and%20in%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20in%20particular.%20For%20lack%20of%20autonomy%20within%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20their%20home%2C%20the%20expression%20of%20this%20political%20consciousness%20in%20the%20public%20space%20is%20immensely%20important%20to%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20and%20to%20their%20sense%20of%20being%2C%20and%20this%20is%20their%20driving%20force.%20While%20this%20is%20their%20strength%2C%20it%20is%20also%20their%20vulnerability%2C%20as%20vested%20interests%20from%20even%20among%20them%2C%20can%20so%20easily%20manipulate%20it%20in%20any%20which%20way.%20There%20is%20enough%20evidence%20coming%20in%20to%20show%20that%20%E2%80%98lines%20were%20crossed%E2%80%99%20and%20extremely%20negative%20roles%20were%20played%20by%20sections%20of%20Meira%20Paibis%20in%20the%20present%20conflict%20and%20that%20at%20certain%20moments%20of%20the%20conflict%20there%20was%20manipulation.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20justification%20for%20these%20roles%2C%20but%20neither%20can%20there%20be%20sweeping%20generalizations%20and%20condemnation%20for%20all.%20The%20question%20then%20is%20how%20to%20%E2%80%98channelise%E2%80%99%20this%20political%20consciousness%20and%20this%20resistance%20to%20stay%20focussed%20on%20a%20community%20enhancing%20rather%20than%20community%20dividing%20approach%2C%20that%20can%20form%20the%20core%20of%20peace%20building%20efforts.%20It%20is%20a%20daunting%20task%20but%20not%20impossible%2C%20and%20very%20tiny%20baby%20steps%20have%20already%20been%20initiated%20quietly%20at%20the%20local%20level%20by%20women%20who%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20or%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Kuki%20side%20we%20also%20met%20and%20interacted%20at%20length%20with%20young%20women%2C%20educated%20in%20Universities%20outside%20Manipur%20but%20who%20are%20now%20back%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20who%20provided%20a%20refreshingly%20different%20and%20gendered%20perspective%20and%20analysis%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20ethnic%20divide%20and%20the%20stereotypical%20role%20of%20men%20in%20general%20including%20men%20from%20their%20own%20community.%20They%20were%20enraged%20that%20men%20who%20cannot%20manage%20their%20personal%20lives%20are%20entrusted%20with%20managing%20the%20country%2C%20with%20the%20mess%20that%20men%20as%20%E2%80%98decision%20makers%E2%80%99%20from%20Delhi%20down%20to%20the%20local%20level%20have%20created%20and%20of%20women%20being%20caught%20in%20between%2C%20and%20having%20to%20attend%20to%20and%20clean%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98mess%E2%80%99!%20These%20women%20were%20grateful%20and%20appreciative%20of%20the%20opportunity%20to%20interact%20with%20our%20team%2C%20air%20their%20frustrations%20and%20share%20their%20thoughts%2C%20as%20they%20were%20fed%20up%20of%20answering%20mechanical%20questions%20posed%20to%20them%20by%20visiting%20media%20teams%20and%20others.%20They%20were%20also%20able%20to%20discuss%20at%20length%20and%20in%20a%20balanced%20and%20unbiased%20manner%20the%20role%20that%20social%20media%20and%20fake%20news%20has%20played%20in%20fuelling%20the%20conflict.%20Many%20of%20the%20older%20women%20also%20felt%20that%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%2C%20of%20having%20appointed%20advisors%20from%20outside%20with%20right%20wing%20links%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20listening%20to%20voices%20from%20the%20ground%20is%20also%20a%20critical%20contributory%20factor%20to%20the%20present%20catastrophe%20and%20to%20determining%20the%20hate%20filled%20political%20narrative%20of%20the%20state%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20SHOULD%20WE%20BE%20THINKING%20ABOUT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Manipur%20has%20witnessed%20several%20episodes%20of%20violent%20conflicts%20over%20the%20years.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20civilisational%20control%20and%20norms%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20lost%2C%20and%20lines%20of%20control%20crossed%20like%20never%20before.%20If%20this%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20has%20been%20pointed%20out%20by%20both%20sides%2C%20then%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Convention%20as%20well%20as%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20Meitei%20War%20principles%20and%20the%20Tribal%20war%20principles%20which%20predate%20Geneva%20have%20been%20grossly%20violated.%20The%20fact%20that%20lines%20have%20been%20crossed%20is%20indeed%20alarming%20as%20is%20indicated%20by%20the%20numerous%20cases%20of%20brutal%20sexual%20violence%20as%20well%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20ambulances%20carrying%20the%20injured%20were%20waylaid%20and%20attacked%20even%20as%20convention%20dictates%20that%20hospitals%20and%20health%20services%20be%20exempt%20from%20attacks%20in%20even%20the%20most%20brutal%20of%20wars.%20These%20tragic%20instances%20raise%20the%20question%20as%20to%20why%20such%20lines%20were%20crossed%3F%20In%20any%20process%20of%20peace%20building%20this%20question%20will%20have%20to%20be%20thoroughly%20probed%20and%20factored%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Killings%20and%20death%20is%20inevitable%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20or%20in%20the%20process%20of%20%E2%80%98defense%E2%80%99%20but%20what%20is%20not%20acceptable%20and%20was%20strongly%20condemned%20across%20sections%20is%20the%20levels%20of%20barbarity.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20initiate%20some%20conversations%20on%20the%20levels%20of%20barbarity%20with%20the%20Meiteis%20but%20it%20was%20only%20with%20the%20more%20progressive%20people.%20More%20in-depth%20engagement%20is%20required%20and%20with%20a%20wider%20cross%20section%20of%20people%20of%20both%20the%20communities%20including%20with%20the%20Meira%20Paibis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20systematic%20clampdown%20on%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20dissenting%20local%20voices%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20and%20the%20promotion%20and%20patronisation%20of%20vigilante%20groups%20that%20toe%20the%20political%20line%20has%20obliterated%20or%20systematically%20suppressed%20an%20important%20section%20of%20credible%20voices%20that%20help%20to%20maintain%20a%20level%20of%20checks%20and%20balances%20that%20keeps%20together%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20communities.%20In%20conflict%20affected%20Manipur%20this%20has%20always%20been%20of%20particular%20significance.%20The%20BJP%20regime%E2%80%99s%20coercive%20approach%20has%20enabled%20the%20hijacking%20of%20rational%20and%20societal%20building%20voices%20by%20the%20divisive%20and%20hate%20filled%20agenda%20of%20the%20state%20supported%20non%20state%20groups.%20The%20blanket%20impunity%20provided%20to%20such%20forces%20and%20select%20CSOs%20by%20the%20State%20has%20totally%20emboldened%20such%20groups%2C%20given%20them%20a%20sense%20of%20complete%20security%20and%20enabled%20them%20and%20not%20the%20progressive%20voices%20to%20control%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20There%20is%20a%20huge%20proliferation%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20ranging%20from%20light%20machine%20and%20combat%20guns%20to%20mortars%20and%20rocket%20launchers.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20the%20arms%20were%20both%20looted%20or%20handed%20over%20upon%20production%20of%20%E2%80%98aadhar%20cards%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20police%20stations%20and%20depots!%20We%20saw%20people%20moving%20around%20with%20AK%2047s%20casually%20slung%20over%20their%20shoulders%20clad%20in%20casuals%20or%20in%20military%20fatigues!%20As%20army%20fatigues%20were%20also%20looted%20and%20widely%20distributed%2C%20oftentimes%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20distinguish%20between%20a%20civilian%20in%20%E2%80%98defense%E2%80%99%20role%20versus%20state%20security%20forces!%20The%20availability%20of%20this%20level%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20in%20a%20state%20with%20an%20extensive%20international%20border%20is%20deeply%20disturbing%20and%20totally%20incomprehensible%20from%20a%20National%20Security%20point%20of%20view.%20It%20totally%20defies%20one%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20and%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98internal%20security%E2%80%99%20and%20of%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Government%20in%20question%20to%20be%20in%20control.%20In%20Manipur%20today%20who%20is%20in%20control%20has%20become%20a%20guessing%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20issue%20of%20%E2%80%98toxic%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20need%20to%20form%20a%20network%20of%20exposed%20young%20men%20from%20both%20communities%20to%20work%20against%20it%20was%20also%20raised%20by%20a%20PhD%20researcher%20%E2%80%93%20a%20young%20man%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20We%20encountered%20shelling%2C%20gunshots%20and%20aggressive%20tear%20gassing%20at%20different%20places%20and%20at%20different%20moments%20of%20our%20visit.%20One%20night%20we%20were%20housed%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20his%20family%20and%20prevented%20from%20going%20back%20to%20our%20hotel%20by%20the%20relentless%20onslaught%20of%20peppered%20tear%20gas%20and%20gunshots%20and%20witnessed%20the%20reaction%20and%20trauma%20of%20his%20little%20children.%20We%20wondered%20about%20the%20collective%20trauma%20of%20children%20across%20the%20ethnic%20divides%20in%20Manipur%20for%20the%20last%20three%20months!%20And%20yet%20instead%20of%20working%20towards%20finding%20a%20sincere%20solution%2C%20it%20is%20whataboutery%20that%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20indulge%20in.%20What%20if%20their%20own%20children%20were%20caught%20up%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20was%20our%20question%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20issue%20of%20illegal%20migration%20of%20people%20from%20across%20the%201700-km-long%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20was%20repeatedly%20mentioned%20as%20a%20key%20trigger%20of%20the%20present%20conflict%20by%20the%20Meiteis.%20There%20were%20allegations%20by%20both%20sides%20that%20border%20management%20which%20lies%20with%20the%20Centre%20is%20pathetically%20run%20or%20deliberately%20mismanaged.%20Picking%20up%20on%20the%20question%20of%20poor%20management%20of%20the%20border%20issues%2C%20the%20Kuki%20leaders%20pointed%20out%20that%20with%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20the%20extensive%20human%20rights%20violations%20by%20the%20military%20junta%2C%20crossing%20over%20of%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20is%20inevitable.%20India%20needs%20to%20urgently%20formulate%20a%20clear%20Refugee%20Policy%20guided%20by%20International%20standards%20and%20play%20a%20role%20on%20Refugee%20protection%20as%20an%20Asian%20leader.%20They%20further%20reiterated%20that%20there%20should%20be%20clear%20guidelines%20to%20identify%20refugees%20so%20that%20genuine%20Indian%20citizens%20are%20not%20repeatedly%20harassed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20immediate%20as%20well%20as%20long%20term%20fallout%20of%20the%20present%20conflict%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20internally%20displaced%20people%2C%20which%20needs%20urgent%20attention.%20In%20the%20relief%20camps%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20relief%20camps%20itself%20and%20the%20horror%20that%20drove%20people%20to%20these%20camps%2C%20the%20large%20looming%20question%20on%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20face%20was%20about%20their%20uncertain%20future%20and%20status.%20The%20issue%20of%20IDPs%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20raised%20by%20human%20rights%20and%20relief%20workers%20in%20the%20past%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20certainly%20calls%20for%20urgently%20pushing%20for%20an%20IDP%20policy%20to%20be%20drafted%20and%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20There%20is%20undoubtedly%20an%20angle%20of%20dwindling%20land%20resources%20and%20increased%20populations%20making%20claims%20on%20the%20limited%20land%20and%20the%20tension%20around%20this.%20An%20opinion%20that%20was%20expressed%20from%20the%20Meitei%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Nagas%20was%20that%20perhaps%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20stop%20the%20%E2%80%98recognition%E2%80%99%20of%20new%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20clear%20cut%20agenda%20of%20bringing%20about%20a%20communal%20divide%20along%20religious%20lines%20by%20the%20right%20wing%20Hindutva%20forces%20was%20strongly%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20Kuki%20side%20with%20documented%20evidence.%20On%20the%20Meitei%20side%2C%20while%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20and%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20(which%20appears%20to%20be%20more%20like%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20private%20army)%20is%20loud%20and%20clear%2C%20opinions%20are%20divided%20about%20the%20actual%20control%20and%20power%20of%20the%20communal%20forces%20over%20the%20Meitei%20ethos.%20Some%20are%20reluctant%20to%20give%20them%20more%20importance%20and%20power%20than%20they%20actually%20have%2C%20some%20wonder%20whether%20they%20can%20be%20used%20while%20yet%20others%20see%20them%20being%20at%20the%20root%20of%20the%20hate%20filled%20agenda.%20Whatever%20be%20the%20various%20opinions%2C%20the%20insidious%20inroads%20of%20Indian%20right%20wing%20forces%20into%20Meitei%20society%2C%20having%20a%20clearcut%20agenda%20especially%20in%20districts%20like%20Bishenpur%2C%20where%20there%20are%20large%20numbers%20of%20followers%20of%20the%20indigenous%20Sanamahi%20faith%20cannot%20be%20trivialized.%20They%20are%20there%20with%20their%20agenda%20advancing%20stealthily%2C%20fraying%20and%20diluting%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20the%20Meitei%20ethos%20and%20sense%20of%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Narco%20Terrorism%20is%20a%20phrase%20that%20is%20bandied%20around%20by%20all%20and%20sundry%20but%20it%20is%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20great%20concern.%20That%20there%20is%20a%20nexus%20between%20the%20politically%20powerful%2C%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20elections%20and%20drug%20cartels%20is%20obvious%20enough%20but%20it%20is%20an%20extremely%20murky%20and%20violent%20world%20and%20beyond%20the%20reach%20of%20common%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESURVIVING%20%3A%20ON%20RELIEF%20AND%20REHABILITATION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20relief%20camps%20in%20Moirang%2C%20Tengnoupal%20and%20Kangpokpi.%20Camps%20in%20Moirang%20had%20mostly%20Meitei%20people%20and%20the%20camps%20in%20other%20two%20places%20had%20displaced%20people%20belonging%20to%20Kuki-Zo%20communities.%20These%20camps%20were%20housed%20in%20school%20and%20college%20premises.%20This%20has%20meant%20that%20educational%20activities%20in%20these%20spaces%20have%20come%20to%20a%20halt%20since%20the%20last%203%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20presence%20appeared%20to%20be%20absent%20or%20minimal%20in%20the%20relief%20Camps.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20when%20the%20conflict%20began%20much%20of%20the%20relief%20arrangements%20were%20being%20done%20by%20community%20groups%20particularly%20the%20localities%20where%20these%20camps%20came%20up.%20In%20fact%20it%20is%20only%20now%2C%203%20months%20later%20that%20the%20state%20is%20attempting%20to%20intervene%20by%20way%20of%20relief.%20However%2C%20the%20relief%20is%20still%20far%20from%20satisfactory.%20The%20living%20conditions%20in%20the%20camps%20continue%20to%20be%20difficult.%20Only%20two%20substantial%20meals%20consisting%20mostly%20of%20rice%20and%20dal%20are%20served%20twice%20a%20day%20and%20not%20much%20is%20provided%20in%20between%2C%20not%20even%20morning%20tea%2C%20which%20the%20people%20have%20expressed%20is%20very%20difficult%20especially%20for%20the%20elderly%20and%20the%20children.%20Children%20have%20no%20access%20to%20other%20snacks.%20Mattresses%20have%20been%20spread%20out%20on%20the%20floors%20of%20the%20rooms%20and%20with%20the%20rains%20the%20rooms%20double%20up%20as%20a%20space%20for%20drying%20clothes.%20This%20makes%20the%20atmosphere%20damp%20and%20poses%20a%20health%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20privacy.%20Men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20are%20sharing%20the%20same%20space.%20Pregnant%20and%20lactating%20mothers%20are%20also%20not%20provided%20separate%20space.%20Mothers%20and%20pregnant%20women%20lacked%20necessities%20such%20as%20thermos%20and%20hot%20water%20bags%20which%20were%20then%20provided%20by%20the%20community%20groups%20in%20some%20places.%20PDS%20provisions%20have%20not%20reached%20the%20camps.%20In%20fact%20PDS%20has%20not%20reached%20the%20districts%20in%20the%20past%203%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20dedicated%20health%20services%20in%20the%20camps%2C%20just%20informal%20arrangements%20with%20locality%20medicine%20shops%20for%20providing%20medicines%20where%20necessary.%20No%20psychosocial%20counseling%20is%20being%20provided%20and%20as%20one%20of%20the%20camp%20persons%20expressed%20that%20she%20feels%20there%20is%20no%20one%20she%20can%20share%20her%20sorrow%20with%20even%20though%20there%20are%20many%20people%20in%20the%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20has%20come%20to%20a%20complete%20halt%20and%20is%20a%20big%20concern%20especially%20for%20parents%20of%20those%20who%20are%20in%20class%2010%20and%2012.%20There%20are%20concerns%20about%20their%20board%20exams%20and%20preparations%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20camp%20members%20have%20also%20expressed%20the%20need%20for%20work%20and%20some%20camp%20residents%20are%20compelled%20to%20leave%20the%20camps%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20Some%20community%20groups%20have%20initiated%20livelihood%20activities%20in%20some%20camps%20but%20have%20expressed%20that%20this%20is%20merely%20a%20stop%20gap%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20persons%20who%20arrived%20at%20the%20camps%20have%20subsequently%20also%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20camps%20and%20are%20residing%20with%20relatives%20in%20the%20state%20or%20outside%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20question%20that%20is%20left%20unanswered%20is%20rehabilitation.%20How%20and%20when%20can%20those%20in%20the%20camps%20safely%20return%3F%20How%20will%20they%20rebuild%20their%20homes%20that%20have%20been%20destroyed%3F%20Many%20including%20community%20relief%20camp%20committee%20members%20are%20raising%20this%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20observations%20and%20information%20gathered%20after%20interactions%20with%20those%20in%20the%20camps%20and%20the%20volunteers%20and%20community%20groups%20the%20following%20suggestions%20are%20being%20made%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM-300x272.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM-1024x928.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668284%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221087%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAN%20THERE%20BE%20ANY%20FINAL%20THOUGHTS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20go%20back%20from%20the%20Manipur%20battleground%20with%20a%20high%20level%20of%20despondency.%20Our%20team%20experienced%20the%20same%20sadness%2C%20depression%20and%20sense%20of%20futility.%20The%20strange%20refusal%20of%20the%20PM%20to%20say%20anything%20till%20pushed%2C%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20the%20apathy%20of%20the%20Centre%20to%20the%20state%20and%20to%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict.%20At%20another%20level%20though%2C%20it%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20militaristic%20strategy%20of%20tiring%20out%20your%20opponents%20by%20making%20them%20%E2%80%98wait%E2%80%99%20it%20out.%20We%20could%20see%20the%20fatigue%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20women%20on%20both%20sides%20who%20were%20out%20protesting%20or%20grappling%20against%20emerging%20crises%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20The%20class%20and%20economic%20dimensions%20of%20peoples%20suffering%20and%20how%20they%20will%20rebuild%20their%20lives%20is%20also%20quite%20apparent.%20Without%20a%20doubt%2C%20it%20is%20the%20poor%20and%20primarily%20the%20rural%20poor%20who%20will%20face%20the%20greatest%20challenge%20in%20rebuilding%20their%20lives%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come.%20That%20peoples%20and%20communities%20are%20expendable%20was%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20seemed%20to%20run%20through%20all%20the%20State%20action%20or%20inaction.%20Yet%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20could%20not%20but%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98spirit%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20continued%20%E2%80%98res