20their%20predetermined%20mould.%20Khawaja%20sings%20for%20the%20Prophet%2C%20then%20how%20can%20he%20enjoy%20such%20a%20lecherous%20song%3F%20Or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20how%20dare%20he%20tap%20into%20his%20femininity%20to%20dance%20like%20his%20favourite%20heroine.%20Sadaf%2C%20a%20producer%20on%20a%20local%20news%20channel%2C%20chances%20upon%20the%20video%20on%20YouTube%20%E2%80%93%20and%20is%20almost%20immediately%20embarrassed%20of%20her%20father.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20when%20they%20first%20go%20home%20after%20discovering%20the%20video%2C%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20confront%20him.%20Her%20husband%20Danish%20(Ali%20Kureshi)%20speaks%20to%20her%20father%2C%20showing%20him%20the%20video%20and%20asking%20him%20about%20it.%20Although%20Sadaf%20could%20be%20part%20of%20the%20intellectual%20elite%2C%20her%20worldview%20proves%20to%20be%20more%20conservative%20than%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%2C%20who%20defends%20his%20father-in-law%20by%20denouncing%20the%20narrow-mindedness%20of%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM-1024x477.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668275%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22559%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Zindagi%20Tamasha%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20interrogates%20a%20society%20riddled%20with%20dogma%20and%20rigidity%2C%20which%20likes%20to%20stifle%20the%20slightest%20hints%20of%20happiness%20and%20pleasure%20that%20isn%E2%80%99t%20prescribed%20by%20it.%20The%20family-like%20neighbours%20start%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20Khawajas.%20The%20wedding%20invitations%20stop%2C%20some%20neighbours%20stop%20greeting%20him%20on%20the%20street%2C%20some%20send%20their%20kids%20to%20the%20doorstep%20when%20he%20goes%20to%20their%20home.%20On%20the%20day%20of%20Eid%2C%20some%20neighbours%20slam%20the%20door%20on%20his%20face%20when%20he%20offers%20them%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehalwa-puri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20we%E2%80%99re%20told%20the%20neighbours%20usually%20looked%20forward%20to.%20For%20all%20intents%20and%20purposes%2C%20the%20upstanding%20Khawaja%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20excommunicated%20by%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emohalla%20wallah%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20premiered%20at%20the%202019%20Busan%20International%20Film%20Festival%2C%20and%20has%20been%20battling%20for%20release%20for%20over%20four%20years.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20happened%20primarily%20because%20of%20one%20scene%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Khawaja%20is%20trying%20to%20record%20a%20video%20for%20a%20public%20apology%20to%20his%20friends%20and%20loved%20ones.%20A%20cleric%20oversees%20this%2C%20constantly%20interrupting%20Khawaja%20by%20saying%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20look%20%E2%80%98remorseful%20enough%E2%80%99.%20Khawaja%20lets%20it%20slide%20a%20few%20times%2C%20but%20slowly%20becomes%20agitated%20by%20the%20cleric%E2%80%99s%20condescension%2C%20and%20slams%20him%20for%20the%20boys%20getting%20sexually%20abused%20by%20clerics%20and%20Imams.%20This%20scene%20became%20the%20point%20of%20contention%20for%20political%20party%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Tehreek-E-Labbaik%2C%20which%20held%20widespread%20protests%2C%20calling%20the%20film%20%E2%80%98blasphemous%E2%80%99.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20years%20in%20eerie%20poetic%20fashion%2C%20much%20like%20his%20protagonist%2C%20even%20Khoosat%20has%20been%20denounced%20by%20religious%20scholars%20and%20given%20death%20threats%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcontroversy-behind-joyland-explained%5C%22%3EWhy%20did%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Oscar%20Pick%20%E2%80%98Joyland%E2%80%99%20Stoke%20Controversy%20in%20the%20Country%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20compelling%20choices%20of%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20that%20its%20protagonist%20is%20no%20saint%20either.%20Khawaja%E2%80%99s%20acquaintance%20%E2%80%93%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20DVD-rental%20shop%2C%20Usman%20(Adeel%20Afzal)%20%E2%80%93%20invites%20him%20to%20a%20gathering.%20When%20he%20reaches%20there%2C%20Khawaja%20finds%20men%20drinking%2C%20while%20an%20effeminate-looking%20man%20(Sarmad%20Khoosat%20himself)%20dances%20for%20them.%20Usman%20tells%20him%20%E2%80%98be%20easy%E2%80%99%2C%20also%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cour%20kind%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahaul%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Usman%20assures%20Khawaja%20that%20no%20one%20would%20judge%20him%20for%20being%20himself.%20Offended%20at%20being%20identified%20as%20gay%2C%20Khawaja%20flings%20many%20homophobic%20slurs%20at%20Usman.%20According%20to%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%2C%20this%20is%20the%20real%20tragedy%20of%20a%20society%20fuelled%20by%20orthodoxy.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Khawaja%20judging%20Usman%2C%20or%20Sadaf%20judging%20her%20own%20father%20%E2%80%93%20everyone%20wants%20to%20be%20more%20pious%20than%20the%20next%20person%2C%20without%20anyone%20trying%20to%20understand%20each%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%