%20if%20asking%20her%20what%20is%20wrong%20about%20being%20himself.%20Khoosat%20also%20showcases%20Khawaja%20as%20a%20petty%20version%20of%20himself%2C%20when%20he%20goes%20and%20tells%20on%20Usman%E2%80%99s%20secret%20gatherings%20to%20the%20local%20police%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20way%20to%20measure%20up%20to%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98man%20of%20faith%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20own%20eyes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20standout%20performance%20of%20the%20film%20is%20Khawaja%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Farkhanda.%20Samiya%20Mumtaz%E2%80%99s%20face%20is%20a%20beacon%20of%20empathy%2C%20grace%20and%20resolve.%20Some%20of%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20finest%20directorial%20touches%20are%20when%20a%20scene%20plays%20and%20he%20cuts%20to%20Farkhanda%20silently%20and%20powerlessly%20absorbing%20the%20events%20around%20her.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20her%20husband%20dancing%20along%20with%20heroines%20on%20TV%20in%20their%20living%20room%3B%20or%20when%20she%20wordlessly%20tries%20to%20be%20there%20for%20her%20daughter%20after%20she%E2%80%99s%20found%20the%20viral%20video.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20scenes%20in%20the%20film%2C%20she%20lies%20to%20him%20telling%20him%20she%20heard%20him%20sing%2C%20despite%20having%20gauged%20from%20his%20face%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20sing%20at%20the%20annual%20festivity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EZindagi%20Tamasha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20chilling%20portrait%20of%20a%20society%20that%20pays%20so%20much%20attention%20to%20the%20wheels%20of%20ideology%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20make%20note%20of%20the%20people%20being%20crushed%20or%20stifled%20under%20it%20everyday.%20Given%20the%20current%20state%20of%20creative%20conservatism%20permeating%20the%20arts%20in%20India%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20circus%20that%20is%20about%20to%20ensue%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20course-correct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3