eak%20in%20the%20recently-concluded%20monsoon%20session%20of%20Parliament.%20A%20range%20of%20Opposition%20MPs%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20took%20turns%20to%20corner%20the%20Union%20government%20by%20identifying%20instances%20and%20issues%20where%20the%20Modi-led%20NDA%20government%20has%20acted%20decidedly%20against%20cooperative%20federalism%2C%20%3Cem%3Esabka%20saath%2C%20sabka%20vikaas%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20scam-free%20governance%2C%20which%20constantly%20feature%20in%20its%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inimitable%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%2C%20questioned%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20poor%20attendance%20in%20Parliament%2C%20lampooning%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9Cif%20not%20Modi%2C%20who%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20Congress%20leader%20Manish%20Tewari%20brought%20out%20references%20to%20highlight%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%20on%20national%20security%20matters%2C%20especially%20the%20continuing%20Chinese%20aggression%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20borders.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20led%20from%20the%20front%20to%20attack%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20arrogance%20and%20indifference%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20sectarian%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20and%20communal%20violence%20in%20Haryana.%20Backing%20the%20INDIA%20MPs%20were%20leaders%20like%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20who%20invoked%20rising%20radicalisation%20among%20Hindus%20in%20India%20while%20speaking%20about%20the%20recent%20selective%20killing%20of%20some%20Muslim%20men%20by%20a%20railway%20cop%20in%20a%20moving%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20the%202023%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20Tells%20Us%20About%20the%20State%20of%20Governance%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmonsoon-session-parliament-laws-discussion%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%202023%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20Tells%20Us%20About%20the%20State%20of%20Governance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20matters%20debatable%2C%20the%20monsoon%20session%20belonged%20to%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20displayed%20rare%20unity%20in%20its%20ranks%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Union%20government%20rushed%20through%2023%20bills%20with%20its%20brute%20majority.%20The%20monsoon%20session%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20first%20test%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20ideological%20unity.%20Through%20the%20course%20of%20the%20session%2C%20INDIA%20MPs%20showed%20that%20the%20Opposition%20grouping%20is%20not%20a%20loose%20coalition%20brought%20together%20without%20a%20plan.%20Its%20leaders%20coordinated%2C%20acted%20and%20performed%20in%20unison.%20They%20met%20daily%20to%20decide%20on%20a%20common%20plan%20of%20action%2C%20unitedly%20appeared%20dressed%20in%20black%20to%20protest%20against%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20Manipur%2C%20and%20even%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Houses%20together.%20More%20importantly%2C%20they%20appeared%20to%20be%20serious%20about%20sticking%20together%20despite%20occasional%20differences%2C%20as%20could%20be%20seen%20when%20all%20of%20them%20eventually%20agreed%20to%20a%20no-trust%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20MPs%20had%20no%20new%20weapon%20in%20their%20armour.%20As%20always%2C%20they%20invoked%20their%20hackneyed%20nationalist%20credentials%2C%20aggressively%20defended%20their%20government%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20contentious%20government%20data%2C%20and%20indulged%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ead%20hominem%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eattacks%20on%20Opposition%20leaders%20without%20feeling%20the%20need%20to%20offer%20a%20fresh%20perspective%2C%20or%20a%20narrative%2C%20in%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3Eprime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20that%20lasted%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20resembled%20most%20of%20his%20previous%20speeches%2C%20including%20his%20focus%20on%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20much%20more%20than%20recounting%20his%20achievements.%20Modi%20and%20his%20ministers%E2%80%99%20attempt%20to%20discount%20INDIA%20as%20%E2%80%9CI.dot%2C%20N.dot%2C%20D.dot%2C%20I.dot%2C%20A.dot%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20speeches%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20dismissing%20the%20newly-formed%20Opposition%20grouping%20as%20%E2%80%9CGhamandiya%E2%80%9D%20reflected%20the%20communication%20crisis%20that%20has%20plagued%20the%20BJP%20ever%20since%20the%20strategically-named%20INDIA%20bloc%20emerged.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20preempted%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20line%20of%20attack%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3Ehit%20out%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Carrogance%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20not%20intervening%20urgently%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20he%20effectively%20nullified%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20constant%20referring%20to%20INDIA%20as%20%E2%80%9CGhamandiya%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98No%20Trace%20of%20Sympathy%E2%80%99%3A%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20Reply%20to%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Parliament%20Was%20an%20Insult%20to%20Manipur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-trace-of-sympathy-modi-shahs-reply-to-the-opposition-in-parliament-was-an-insult-to-manipur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98No%20Trace%20of%20Sympathy%E2%80%99%3A%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20Reply%20to%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Parliament%20Was%20an%20Insult%20to%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20session%20gave%20a%20significant%20operational%20window%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20devise%20ways%20to%20work%20together.%20They%20seemed%20to%20rectify%20the%20mistakes%20they%20had%20made%20in%20their%20previous