0in%20Nuh%2C%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20broke%20out%20in%20Nuh%20and%20spread%20over%20the%20district%20on%20July%2031%2C%20when%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20took%20out%20a%20%E2%80%98Shobha%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20through%20Muslim-majority%20areas%20carrying%20weapons%20and%20allegedly%20used%20provocative%20slogans.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbittu-bajranji-runs-as-plainclothed-cops-chase-with-sticks-in-dramatic-video-before-arrest-101692144063870.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20was%20present%20at%20the%20rally%20and%20allegedly%20snatched%20weapons%20from%20policement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fnuh-violence-bajrang-dal-member-bittu-bajrangi-arrested-from-faridabad-8894069%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20video%20of%20the%20arrest%20shows%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20attempting%20to%20flee%20while%20around%2020%20policemen%20in%20plain%20clothes%20chase%20and%20eventually%20capture%20him%20in%20Faridabad%E2%80%99s%20Dabua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu%20Bajrangi%E2%80%99s%20real%20name%20is%20Raj%20Kumar.%20He%20is%20the%20Faridabad%20chief%20of%20the%20Gau%20Raksha%20Bajrang%20Force.%20In%20several%20videos%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20he%20has%20been%20seen%20to%20be%20making%20anti-Muslim%20remarks%20and%20even%20encouraging%20the%20use%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20against%20him%20was%20registered%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20ASP%20Usha%20Kundu%20at%20Sadar%20Nuh%20police%20station%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20include%20assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20a%20public%20servant%20from%20discharge%20of%20duty%2C%20voluntarily%20causing%20harm%20to%20deter%20a%20public%20worker%20from%20doing%20duty%2C%20rioting%2C%20and%20Section%2025%20of%20the%20Arms%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20July%2031%2C%20during%20my%20duties%20related%20to%20maintaining%20law%20and%20order%20for%20the%20Jal%20Abhishek%C2%A0Yatra%2C%20around%2012.30%20pm%2C%20300%20metres%20away%20from%20Nalhar%20temple%2C%20I%20encountered%20a%20group%20of%2015-20%20individuals%20going%20towards%20the%20temple.%20We%20had%20asked%20people%20not%20to%20carry%20weapons%20during%20the%20yatra%20and%20during%20a%20peace%20committee%20meeting%2C%20this%20was%20reiterated%20to%20organisers%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ASP%20said%20in%20her%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20them%20were%20carrying%20swords%20and%20trident-like%20weapons.%20With%20the%20assistance%20of%20my%20staff%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20using%20these%20weapons%20and%20causing%20harm.%20One%20individual%2C%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%2C%20identified%20through%20social%20media%2C%20along%20with%20his%20associates%2C%20attempted%20to%20snatch%20these%20weapons%20from%20my%20fellow%20police%20officers%20and%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20seized%20these%20weapons%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20police%20force%20and%20brought%20them%20to%20our%20official%20vehicle.%20Bajrangi%20and%20his%20associates%20then%20sat%20in%20front%20of%20my%20official%20vehicle%20and%20began%20shouting%20slogans%20against%20the%20police%E2%80%A6%20(They)%20broke%20the%20rear%20window%E2%80%A6%20took%20away%20the%20seized%20weapons%20and%20threatened%20police%20officers.%20They%20acted%20against%20the%20law%20by%20using%20illegal%20weapons%20and%20threatening%20behaviour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20complaint%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2015-20%20people%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20charged%20under%20various%20sections%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrangi%20had%20been%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20month%20for%20a%20p