ve%20remaining%20issues%20expeditiously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019th%20round%20of%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20corps%20commander-level%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20Chushul-Moldo%20meeting%20point%20on%20August%2013-14.%20The%20meeting%20ended%20at%20around%205%3A30%20pm%20on%20Monday%2C%20but%20it%20took%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20for%20the%20two%20sides%20to%20release%20a%20joint%20press%20release.%20There%20had%20been%20no%20joint%20statement%20issued%20after%20the%20last%20round%20of%20military%20talks%20held%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20is%20significant%20as%20it%20takes%20place%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20scheduled%20to%20travel%20to%20Delhi%20for%20the%20annual%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20summit.%20Ahead%20of%20that%2C%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20meet%20Xi%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20next%20week%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20press%20release%20claimed%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Chad%20a%20positive%2C%20constructive%20and%20in-depth%20discussion%20on%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20remaining%20issues%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20Western%20Sector%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20said%20there%20was%20an%20exchange%20of%20views%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Copen%20and%20forward-looking%20manner%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cin%20line%20with%20the%20guidance%20provided%20by%20the%20leadership%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Asian%20neighbours%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20to%20resolve%20the%20remaining%20issues%20in%20an%20expeditious%20manner%20and%20maintain%20the%20momentum%20of%20dialogue%20and%20negotiations%20through%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20channels%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20India%20and%20China%20reiterated%20that%20that%20while%20the%20issues%20were%20being%20resolved%2C%20they%20will%20%E2%80%9Cmaintain%20the%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20border%20areas%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20stand-off%20at%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20since%20May%202020%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20major%20hand-to-hand%20clash%20at%20Galwan%20valley%20that%20left%2024%20soldiers%20dead.%20Since%20then%20there%20have%20been%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20talks%20which%20led%20to%20disengagement%20at%20around%20four%20friction%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20strategic%20areas%20of%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20have%20stalemated%20the%20talks.%20China%20has%20been%20urging%20India%20to%20move%20beyond%20the%20stand-off%20and%20discuss%20these%20two%20remaining%20issues%20as%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20boundary%20question.%20However%2C%20India%20has%20so%20far%20insisted%20that%20the%20stand-off%20cannot%20be%20resolved%20till%20the%20armies%20disengage%20at%20these%20two%20points%20and%20the%20traditional%20patrolling%20points%20in%20the%20area%20are%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20former%20Indian%20ambassador%20to%20China%20Ashok%20Kantha%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAny%20resolution%20must%20involve%20restoration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20pre-May%202020%20patrolling%20rights%20at%20all%20%E2%80%98friction%20points%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20merely%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%98buffer%20zones%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIndia-China%20Corps%20Commanders%E2%80%99%20Meeting%20on%20border%20standoff%20concludes%20without%20breakthrough%20on%20disengagement%20in%20Dapsang%20and%20Demchok.%20Any%20resolution%20must%20involve%20restoration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20pre-May%202020%20patrolling%20rights%20at%20all%20%E2%80%98friction%20points%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20merely%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%98buffer%20zones%E2%80%99.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUnnvhPGc5o%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUnnvhPGc5o%3C%2F