tially%20not%20doing%20well.%20Paying%20Rs%20300%20to%20just%20travel%20from%20North%20Bombay%20to%20South%20Bombay%20and%20an%20additional%20Rs%20300%20to%20perform%20an%20open%20mic%20set%20at%20the%20Canvas%20Laugh%20Club%20initially%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20a%20worthwhile%20pursuit.%20Naturally%2C%20some%20doubts%20had%20begun%20to%20creep%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAllaying%20my%20doubts%2C%20comics%20like%20Sapan%20and%20Kaneez%20(Surka)%20were%20kind%20enough%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20break%20it%20%5Bbeing%20gay%5D%20down%20for%20straight%20people%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20concept%20of%20top%20and%20bottom%20means%E2%80%99%3B%20or%20%E2%80%98They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20Grindr%20is.%20They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20have%20no%20idea%20about%20queer%20people%20in%20this%20country%20and%20how%20they%20live%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20pointers%20made%20sense.%20My%20first%20idea%20was%20that%20the%205-minute%20set%20has%20to%20become%20a%2010-minute%20one%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20break%20everything%20down%20slowly%2C%20and%20therein%20the%20humour%20came%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20special%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20Navin%20explaining%20top%20and%20bottom%20%5Bsex%20positions%5D%20to%20people.%20These%20jokes%20are%20the%20outcome%20of%20trialling%20them%20for%20years%20before%20implementing%20them%20in%20real%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20when%20I%20say%20jokes%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Kerala%20is%20bottom%2C%20Delhi%20is%20top%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20back%20to%20the%20audience%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20inbuilt%20joke%20as%20well.%20The%20demographic%20of%20the%20country%20also%20is%20very%20vivid%20in%20terms%20of%20sexual%20preferences.%20The%20%E2%80%98top%20and%20bottom%E2%80%99%20joke%20has%20become%20a%20reel%20on%20my%20Instagram%20handle.%20If%20you%20read%20the%20comments%20section%20right%20now%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20full%20of%20gay%20people%20trying%20to%20hook%20up%20with%20each%20other.%20What%20I%20like%20about%20queer%20culture%20is%20that%20we%20somehow%20find%20a%20way%20to%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Navin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20straights%20to%20gay%20school.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20full%20special%20is%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMl5xm3p3OW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMl5xm3p3OW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Navin%20Noronha%20(%40HouseOfNoronha)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHouseOfNoronha%2Fstatus%2F1673571572509208576%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20finding%20new%20avenues%20to%20tell%20jokes%2C%20Navin%20has%20over%20the%20span%20of%20his%20career%20found%20a%20way%20to%20completely%20embrace%20his%20lived%20experiences.%20Early%20on%2C%20there%20was%20trepidation%20about%20revealing%20his%20past%20and%20the%20circumstances%20he%20was%20raised%20in.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20people%20about%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20chawl%20in%20Golibar%20road%2C%20Santa%20Cruz%20(East)%2C%20until%20the%20age%20of%207%20and%20moving%20out%20to%20Bhayandar%2C%20an%20unfashionable%20suburb%20outside%20Mumbai%2C%20because%20everybody%20looked%20down%20upon%20these%20places.%20In%20the%20early%20days%2C%20Navin%20argues%20how%20the%20comedy%20scene%20in%20the%20city%20was%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20elite-%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295229%2Ftaj-icecream-mumbai-eatery-loved-by-madhubala-makes-natural-icecream-in-wooden-barrels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Bombay%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Bandra%20boys%20talking%20about%20their%20Tinder%20issues%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20stepped%20into%20comedy%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20them%20that%20I%20was%20from%20Bhayandar.%20But%20then%20the%20more%20I%20delved%20into%20my%20queer%20self%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20my%20reality.%20I%20was%20born%20in%20a%20chawl%20and%20I%20did%20have%20to%20take%20a%20bucket%20to%20a%20common%20toilet%20stall%20every%20morning.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20reality%20of%20so%20many%20people%20in%20the%20city.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20deny%20it.%20The%20more%20I%20owned%20up%20to%20that%20reality%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20on%20me%20to%20be%20truthful%20as%20well%20as%20funny%20by%20tagging%20a%20punch%20line%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvbqq6soJdD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvbqq6soJdD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvbqq6soJdD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Navin%20Noronha%20(%40houseofnoronha)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Apne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20special%20%E2%80%98The%20Good%20Child%E2%80%99%2C%20Navin%20narrates%20a%20hilarious%20story%20from%20his%20childhood%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20chawl%20in%20Golibar%20road.%20In%20this%20particular%20segment%2C%20he%20recalled%20how%20there%20were%20just%20five%20common%20toilets%20for%20hundreds%20of%20families%20living%20in%20his%20chawl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20one%20morning%20as%20a%20five-year-old%2C%20Navin%20stepped%20out%20with%20a%20bucket%20of%20water%20and%20walked%20towards%20the%20common%20toilet%20stalls%20to%20do%20his%20business.%20Unable%20to%20control%20his%20bowels%2C%20however%2C%20he%20released%20portions%20of%20his%20excrement%20along%20the%20passageway.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20a%20collection%20of%2010%20neighbourhood%20aunties%20stood%20outside%20his%20home%20complaining%20to%20his%20mother%20about%20what%20he%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hilariously%20denying%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20Navin%E2%80%99s%20mother%20tells%20him%20something%20that%20he%20would%20hear%20again%20years%20later%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(do%20whatever%20you%20want%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20your%20private%20space%2C%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20outside)%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20he%20finally%20found%20the%20courage%20to%20come%20out%20and%20introduce%20his%20partner%20to%20his%20mother%20at%2027%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reject%20his%20queer%20identity%2C%20but%20did%20say%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20and%20it%20was%20Pride%20Month%20in%20Mumbai.%20Navin%20and%20his%20partner%20were%20photographed%20kissing%20each%20other%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20%3Cem%3EBombay%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20a%20cousin%20he%20dislikes%2C%20a%20screenshot%20of%20that%20photo%20was%20shared%20on%20the%20family%20WhatsApp%20group.%20Furious%20at%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20extended%20family%20finding%20out%20that%20her%20son%20is%20gay%2C%20Navin%E2%80%99s%20mother%20once%20again%20repeated%20that%20maxim%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20kicked%20him%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20Despite%20the%20initial%20pain%2C%20there%20was%20also%20a%20sense%20of%20relief%20for%20Navin.%20He%20and%20his%20partner%20ended%20up%20finding%20an%20apartment%20and%20started%20living%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20called%20a%20pioneer%20of%20queer%20comedy%20or%20anything%20like%20that.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20queer%20community.%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying%20this%20is%20my%20story%20and%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20we%20can%20relate%20on%20different%20issues%20and%20share%20in%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20happiness%20or%20misery.%20The%20bit%20on%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Apne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20not%20just%20a%20queer%20thing%2C%20but%20represents%20a%20much%20bigger%20picture%20of%20how%20South%20Asian%20kids%20live.%20If%20people%20can%20connect%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20coming%20out%20to%20your%20parents%20at%20any%20level%20is%20difficult%2C%20then%20we%E2%80%99ve%20won%20on%20that%20front%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20108