20Rs%2012%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20which%20was%20earlier%20zero!%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20numerous%20herders%20are%20including%20camels%20in%20their%20groups%20because%20they%20can%20once%20again%20make%20money%20from%20them.%20At%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Pushkar%20%3Cem%3Emela%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20price%20of%20camels%20in%20the%20local%20market%20also%20increased%20to%20Rs%2035%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakriti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Genaram%20Raika%2C%20a%20camel%20herder%2C%20has%20been%20dependent%20on%20these%20animals%20for%20livelihood%20since%20childhood.%20When%20man-made%20machinery%20replaced%20camels%20on%20farms%2C%20the%2050-year-old%20was%20also%20unable%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20by%20selling%20milk.%20But%20today%2C%20he%20is%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%2048%2C000%20a%20month%20with%20his%20450%20camels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20there%20was%20little%20awareness%20about%20camel%20milk%2C%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20throw%20it.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20fetch%20good%20income%20by%20selling%2040%20litres%20of%20milk%20every%20day.%20I%20am%20able%20to%20feed%20my%20family%20of%20seven%20with%20this%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20impact%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20Aakriti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20all%20this%20would%20be%20possible%20when%20I%20started.%20But%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20I%20chose%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20village.%20While%20my%20parents%20wanted%20me%20to%20be%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20live%20with%20these%20camel-raising%20communities.%20Through%20this%20job%2C%20I%20can%20now%20address%20the%20very%20issues%20within%20the%20community%20that%20I%20initially%20aimed%20to%20highlight%20during%20my%20time%20as%20a%20journalism%20student!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Aakriti%20Srivastava%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp